Grant Tinsley, PhD wrote an article for Healthline about Reishi mushrooms health benefits for our immune systems.  Some of the main points are: -Test-tube studies have shown that reishi can affect the genes in white blood cells, which are critical parts of your immune system. -What's more, these studies have found that some forms of reishi may alter inflammation pathways in white blood cells. -Research in cancer patients has shown that some of the molecules found in the mushroom can increase the activity of a type of white blood cell called natural killer cells.(Natural killer cells fight infections and cancer in the body.) -Although most immune system benefits of reishi mushroom have been seen in those who are ill, some evidence has shown that it can help healthy people, too. -In one study, the fungus improved lymphocyte function, which helps fight infections and cancer, in athletes exposed to stressful conditions.  Our double extracts are made from fresh Reishi mushrooms we've grown, harvested and processed on our farm.  The extracts are shelf-stable so they are great to have on hand for when you want to easily add them to a daily beverage like morning coffee or afternoon tea. Vorrei tornare qui...due mesi fa...liberi, senza pensieri e senza questo marasma nel mondo! In questa settimana ho visto di tutto, sembrava di essere dentro un film, uno di quei film che ti fanno stare con il fiato sospeso! Aria tesa, il panico nei visi delle persone, nessuno che ti guarda in faccia, strade deserte, supermercati svaligiati, aver paura di starnutire, aver paura di tossire...e soprattutto non sapere cosa ci attende! Sperare di non ammalarci in massa per far si che i posti negli ospedali non finiscano, stare attenti a tutto, niente posti affollati, abitudini stravolte! Noi, noi che abbiamo tutto, non siamo abituati a vivere nella difficolta, perche alla prima difficolta ci buttiamo giu sentendoci piccoli come formiche! Non avrei mai voluto dover spiegare a Johann del perche di tutto questo...non avrei mai voluto fargli vivere un clima del genere..ma eccoci qua! Ne usciremo, forse un po' ammaccati, ma sicuramente piu forti e consapevoli di prima! Oggi abbiamo fatto una passeggiata nella natura, e stato bellissimo...fatelo anche voi! O BLEND QUATRO LADROES da Laszlo foi desenvolvido com oleos essenciais de destacadas propriedades antissepticas e purificadoras, inspirada nos efeitos medicinais e espirituais do famoso "vinagre dos quatro ladroes". Uma lendaria formula de nome "Four Thieves" ou "Quatro Ladroes", permeia lendas e mitos na Europa desde a Antiguidade. Conta-se a lenda que durante a peste bubonica, quatro ladroes desenvolveram uma receita composta por vinagre e alho, que lhes fornecia protecao contra a peste, enquanto saqueavam os corpos das vitimas da doenca. Uma segunda teoria afirma que a formula "anti-peste" foi desenvolvida por Richard Forthave e, originalmente, o "remedio" passou a ser chamado de Forthave's. Com o passar do tempo, no entanto, fomentado por lendas populares, o nome foi substituido para Four Thieves, quatro ladroes em ingles. Este blend e altamente antisseptico, pode ser empregado em difusores de ambiente ou ser diluido em vinagre (para ficar mais semelhante ao original) e ser borrifado em ambientes, ou ainda utilizado na limpeza residencial.  BLENDS: do ingles "misturas", blends sao combinacoes 100% naturais de oleos essenciais e oleos absolutos, com o intuito de recriar aromas raros ou de dificil obtencao. Na forma do blend, estas notas aromaticas sao alcancadas tendo um valor muito mais acessivel, sem perda da qualidade olfativa, podendo ser empregadas na perfumaria e aromaterapia.  COMPOSICAO: - Oleo essencial de cravo-da-india (Syzygium aromaticum) - Oleo essencial de alecrim (Rosmarinus officinalis) - Oleo essencial de eucalipto (Eucalyptus globulus) - Oleo essencial de limao (Citrus limon) - Oleo essencial de canela (Cinamomum ssp)  #aromaterapia #aromatologia #aromacologia #coronavirus #aromatherapie #aromatherapy #aromaterapias #oleosessenciais #essentialoils #essentialoil #terapiasholisticas #terapiaholistica #oleoessencial #terapiaintegrativa #dafnemeris #dafnemerisaromaterapeuta #plantasmedicinais #fitoterapia #autoestima #autocompaixao #bemestar #saudemental #terapiaholisticaintegrativa

*OLEOS ESSENCIAIS ANTIVIRAIS E O CORONAVIRUS*  Trecho de "Oleos essenciais antivirais" do Dr. Jean Pierre Willem - Editora Laszlo  Nas ultimas semanas um assunto alardeia pautas em todo o globo: o coronavirus e a possibilidade de iminencia de uma pandemia.  Acompanhe um trecho da obra "Oleos essenciais antivirais", onde o Dr. Jean Pierre Willem aborda o assunto, elucidando o que e o coronavirus, quais sao os seus reais perigos e quais oleos essenciais podem auxiliar no cuidado da patologia. "A urgencia do momento foi - e ainda e - o coronavirus da sindrome respiratoria do Oriente Medio (MERS-CoV, para Middle-East respiratory syndrome coronavirus; SROM-CoV, sindrome respiratoria por coronavirus do Oriente Medio, anteriormente; e NCoV, para o novo coronavirus). Essa variante de coronavirus altamente patogenica, descoberta em 2012, causa, em particular, um sintoma de pneumonia aguda. O coronavirus (do latim, coroa virus) e o nome de um genero de virus da familia dos Coronaviridae.  Os virus desse tipo, bem como os virus da gripe, podem infectar uma ou mais especies animais e os seres humanos e, dependendo de certas mutacoes, passar de uma especie para outra. Esses virus, as vezes, tornam-se de maneira inabitual patogenicos, por exemplo, devido ao sistema imunologico do novo  hospedeiro (humano ou animal) nao estar adaptado (...) De acordo com dados epidemiologicos disponiveis, a variante NCoV de coronavirus apareceu no Oriente Medio, na Peninsula Arabica. Estudos mostraram que o gene de um virus conhecido por infectar morcegos do tipo pipistrellus difere do NCoV apenas em 1,8%. O estudo de mais de 50 especies de morcegos do genero pipistrellus na Peninsula Arabica e o uso de agua de grota e de guano93 de morcegos sugerem fortemente que este coronavirus encontrou la a sua origem. CORONAVIRUS, WHATS THE DEAL? [?] [?] With all the media hype going on do you need to be worried? [?] [?] *Coronaviruses are found in both animals & humans. Usually, they cause common cold like illnesses. [?] *The SARS & MERS outbreak were both coronaviruses. [?] *The current (Wuhan coronavirus) is new and causes mild symptoms or more severe respiratory illness (pneumonia), fever, cough & difficulty breathing.[?] *As it stands currently, this virus appears to be milder than SARS.[?] *The coronavirus cases have been linked to the South China Seafood Wholesale Market, in Wuhan. But while some sea-going mammals can carry coronaviruses (such as the Beluga whale), the market also has live wild animals, including chickens, bats, rabbits, snakes, which are more likely to be the source. Researchers say the new virus is closely related to one found in Chinese horseshoe bats. However, this does not mean wild bats are the source of the outbreak - they could have passed the virus onto another species sold at the market.[?] *To reduce risk of contracting it; avoid contact with sick people, avoid contact with live stock/farm animals if in risk areas (ie. China) [?]& WASH YOUR HANDS!  *There is lots of media coverage on this at present but it appears to be milder & less lethal than SARS. [?] *The elderly appear to be more at risk of developing complications and less able to fight it off.[?] *Based on what we know so far, this virus MAY be more contagious BUT less deadly. Lupus (also known as systemic lupus erythematosus) is an autoimmune disease, which means that it causes your immune system to turn against tissues and organs throughout your body. Known to trigger major health problems (including kidney disease, neurological dysfunction, and rheumatoid arthritis), lupus can set off inflammation and can cause damage to the heart, lungs, blood vessels, brain, joints, skin, kidneys, and other parts of the body. Chlorophyll is a chemoprotein commonly known for its contribution to the green pigmentation in plants, and is related to protoheme, the red pigment of blood. It can be obtained from green leafy vegetables (broccoli, Brussel sprouts, cabbage, lettuce, and spinach), algae (Chlorella and Spirulina), wheat grass, and numerous herbs (alfalfa, damiana, nettle, and parsley). Chlorophyll has been used traditionally to improve bad breath and other forms of body odor including odors of the urine, feces, and infected wounds. More recently chlorophyll has been used to aid in the removal of various toxins via the liver. Scientific research has demonstrated it may be an effective therapeutic agent in the treatment of herpes simplex, benign breast disease, chemoprevention, tuberculosis, and rheumatoid arthritis. Type 2 diabetes and obesity are also being explored as areas where chlorophyll can also be used.  CONTACT ME DR. The outbreak of coronavirus that originated in Wuhan City, China, is being closely monitored around the world.     Earlier this month, the Coronavirus Study Group of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses formally designated the virus severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV2).     That same day, @WHO gave the disease caused by that virus the name COVID-19.     Under guidelines agreed upon by the WHO, the World Organisation for Animal Health, and the Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations, the name COVID-19 was specifically chosen to avoid association with any particular geographical location, animal, or individual or group of people.     Clinical knowledge about COVID-19 also continues to grow. Among the issues currently under investigation, the effect of SARS-CoV2 on pregnant women and their fetuses is a critical concern; members of the coronavirus family are capable of causing severe complications during pregnancy.     Because SARS-CoV2 has the potential for similar behavior, systemic screening for any suspected infection during pregnancy is recommended.    #doctor  #corona #coronavirus #coronavirusitalianews

The United States has reopened its market to fresh Brazilian beef exports effective immediately. The U.S. stopped Brazilian fresh beef imports in June of 2017, alleging that some shipments failed to pass food safety checks.                    Brazil is one of the largest beef producers globally, exporting $7.3 billion in industrialised and fresh beef products last year. According to USDA data, the United States are the second largest beef importer worldwide, with approximately 1,390 tons cwt imported in 2019.                    The approval to export Brazilian beef to the United States represents a very important achievement to local producers and may unlock new opportunities on countries with similar sanitary requirements, improving Brazilian exports capillarity in the global market. Though the measure will take effect immediately, there are some necessary steps that need to be completed. This includes the Brazilian government sending a list of beef packers that are approved to export to the US. Source: The Rio Times / Reuters / USDA

El Bicarbonato de Sodio quita gran parte de los peligrosos residuos de pesticidas y quimicos que se han incrustado en la superficie de frutas y verduras, cuyo efecto a mediano y largo plazo puede ser letal para la salud puesto que pueden provocar diversas enfermedades degenerativas, tales como el cancer y el diabetes.  _ Modo de preparacion: Por cada litro y medio de  agua, se agrega 1 cucharada de bicarbonato. Se mezcla bien y se colocan en remojo las frutas y hortalizas, aproximadamente 10min, con el fin de eliminar los quimicos. Luego se enjuaga con con agua corriente y estaran listas para su consumo.  #saludable #coronavirus  #comidasaludable #comesano #comidasana #saludable #vidasaludable #comidasaludable #receta #habitossaludables #cocinasaludable #soysaludable #saludablefit #recetascaseras #recetasdecocina #nutricionsaludable #vivirsaludable #consejosaludable #remediocasero

Plague superstition  With all the talk of pandemic this week, it seems like a good time to look in to plagues of the past. Both the Black Death (1348) and the Great Plague (1664) fostered some bizarre ideas about medicine and health. During the Black Death, some people were convinced that the affliction was a punishment from God. To counteract this, they tried to rid themselves of so-called 'heretics' in society - this unfortunately lead to the execution of prostitutes, criminals and other purveyors of 'sin'. Harrowingly, in some European countries, it also prompted a massacre of Jews, as they seemed to be less affected by the disease (probably because they didn't use the common wells) and so were purported as the cause of  it.  Medicine at the time was still very much based on the Greek system of 'balancing the humours' (I will post about this another time) and so there was very little understanding of the spread of infection. There are medical records that have survived that recommend rubbing a mixture of tree-sap and human excrement into the pustules or open sores in order to treat them  Nothing improved in the 300 or so years between the Black Death and the Plague - this time, people blamed the pestilence on: - the planetary positions  - wearing pointy shoes - beastiality - 'miasma' or foul smells The miasma theory basically said that disease was caused by foul smell or infected mists. Whilst we now know this not to be true, it's probably rooted in the idea that smelly decomposing bodies would be covered in rats, rats covered in fleas and the fleas riddled with disease! Many people believed that to inhale this odour would infect you. In some cases, people would build their houses without windows on the side that faced large cities, to avoid the miasma permeating their house! An example of this is Chenies Manor in Amersham Treatement had also not improved, as it was accepted that the best cure for the plague was to drink a glass of your own urine, twice a day!  #history #superstition #folklore #myth #legend #medicine #health #disease #corona #coronavirus #covid_19

Iniziammo a messaggiare, poi la invitai al derby del 10 marzo 2002 e mi disse che sarebbe venuta. Il sabato sera pero la sorella mi scrisse che Ilary forse non poteva venire e per me fu il gelo perche avevo preparato una maglia speciale per lei all'insaputa di tutti. Con i miei amici decisi la frase 'sei unica' anche se non eravamo mai usciti insieme e non c'era mai stato un bacio. Quando seppi che non poteva venire, non dormi tutta la notte e pensai che il destino era contro. Domenica mattina a mezzogiorno e mezzo le scrissi un messaggio 'ciao come stai' e lei non rispose. Pranzai con il telefonino vicino, poi alle 13.30 mi scrisse 'sono sul treno e sto venendo a vedere la partita'. Zompai sul letto come un bambino, sembravo uno stupido. Um estudo sobre a autacao da MICROFISIOTERAPIA no sistema imune foi aceito pela revista cientifica International Journal of Science and Research Methodology, revista internacional de acesso livre dedicada aos mais recentes avancos em pesquisa cientifica.  O objetivo do estudo foi de verificar os efeitos da Microfisioterapia sobre o sistema imunologico em ratos submetidos a um estresse agudo.                      Utilizamos 3 grupos:  G1 - microfisioterapia, ao qual os ratos passaram por uma sessao de microfisioterapia para diagnosticar as origens das disfuncoes e para tratatamento;  G2 - placebo, em que os ratos foram submetidos a uma caricia sobre o dorso por uma pessoa que nao participou do estudo;  G3 - controle, onde nenhuma intervencao foi realizada nestes ratos.  Os ratos foram submetidos a situacoes continuas de estresse.Para a analise da acao do sistema imunologico, foi verificado por citometria, as citocinas IL-2, IL-4 e TNFa nos periodos de 3, 7 e 21 dias apos a aplicacao da tecnica.                     Como previsto, as citocinas aumentaram apos a inducao do estresse agudo, principalmente a IL-4 e o TFNa. Foi verificado que apos 21 dias da intervencao, houve uma reducao significativa no grupo G1 quando comparado com os grupos G2 e G3 para as citocinas IL-4 e TNFa. . Tais citocinas activam os mecanismos inflamatorios moleculares que induzem Neurotoxicidade.  Isto sugere que a microfisioterapia utilizada para tratar os animais foi eficaz em termos de controle da liberacao da IL-4 e do TNFa pelas celulas, assim, essa tecnica influenciou o sistema imunologico em termos de tratamento do mecanismo de estresse agudo.  Apesar desse estudo ter sido realizado em ratos, o mesmo tem se observado nos pacientes humanos tratados com a tecnica. . . Spetsifika opredeleniia infektsii  2019-nCoV zakliuchaetsia v sleduiushchem:   Podozritel'nyi na infektsiiu, vyzvannuiu 2019-nCoV, sluchai: * nalichie klinicheskikh proiavlenii ostroi respiratornoi infektsii, bronkhita, pnevmonii v sochetanii so sleduiushchimi dannymi epidemiologicheskogo anamneza;   * poseshchenie za poslednie 14 dnei do poiavleniia simptomov epidemiologicheski neblagopoluchnykh po 2019-nCoV stran i regionov (glavnym obrazom g. Ukhan', Kitai);   * nalichie tesnykh kontaktov za poslednie 14 dnei s litsami, nakhodiashchimisia pod nabliudeniem po infektsii, vyzvannoi novym koronavirusom2019-nCoV, kotorye v posleduiushchem zaboleli;   * nalichie tesnykh kontaktov za poslednie 14 dnei s litsami, u kotorykh laboratorno podtverzhden diagnoz 2019-nCoV.   Veroiatnyi sluchai infektsii, vyzvannoi 2019-nCoV: * nalichie klinicheskikh proiavlenii tiazheloi pnevmonii, ORDS, sepsisa v sochetanii s dannymi epidemiologicheskogo anamneza.   Podtverzhdennyi sluchai infektsii, vyzvannoi 2019-nCoV: * nalichie klinicheskikh proiavlenii ostroi respiratornoi infektsii, bronkhita, pnevmonii v sochetanii s dannymi epidemiologicheskogo anamneza;   * polozhitel'nye rezul'taty laboratornykh testov na nalichie RNK 2019-nCoV metodom PTsR.   Ob osobennostiakh profilaktiki i lecheniia infektsii chitaite v sleduiushchikh postakh!

En Chine a Beijing (Pekin), surpris par une averse violente, je me refugie dans un petit restaurant de quartier. Je croise le regard souriant d'un homme qui a une bouille particuliere. J'aime beaucoup cette facon d'etre des Chinois qui respirent la joie de vivre et se pretent spontanement a la photo ! C'est l'epidemie actuelle du coronavirus qui m'incite a reposter cette photographie. La determination des Chinois, les moyens qu'ils mettent en oeuvre, leur reactivite et leur discipline collective pour maitriser la situation, est incroyable et quasiment inconcevable en France ou les gens ont un temperament indiscipline, rebelle et individualiste. Au-dela de cette observation, il faut aller en Chine pour comprendre et vivre l'evolution du monde aujourd'hui.  #instaportrait #portraits_shots  #portraitoftheday #onedayoneportrait #portrait #portraitphotography #china #asian  #chine #man  #portraits  #chinois  #beijing  #pekin  #photoshooting #coronavirus

!Buenas tardes foodies! En este post os llevamos hasta Palma de Mallorca, un lugar precioso para pasar las vacaciones. El restaurante al que fuimos se llama Hungry gastro food bar (@hungrygastrofoodbar) [?]Probamos: - Tagliatelle Alfredo con espinacas y pinones - Solomillo de cerdo, patatas caseras, champinones portobello y mayonesa de higos - Palomitas de pollo con ensaladilla de brocoli - Tarta de queso Es un pequeno local regentado por dos hermanos hungaros que decidieron abrir hace unos meses despues de dedicarse durante muchos anos a la hosteleria en Espana. Tienen una carta corta, pero centrandose en la calidad del producto que sirven. El servicio es muy destacable, preocupandose por si todo nos estaba gustando, cambio de cubiertos entre platos... En cuanto a la comida, destacamos su cuidada presentacion, entra por los ojos nada mas verlo. Las palomitas de pollo llevan una corteza semicrujiente donde se pueden apreciar los trozos de palomitas. Nos parecio un plato muy curioso e ideal para empezar.  La cantidad de los tagliatelle es muy generosa y traen pechuga de pollo. La salsa esta muy buena y combina muy bien con los pinones. El solomillo de cerdo viene por defecto al punto, pero se puede hacer mas si se desea. Nos gusto mucho, la carne tierna, las patatas caseras y la salsa de higos le da un toque diferente. Y para acabar, la tarta de queso lleva una fina base de galleta, muy suave y con buena consistencia. El detalle de los arandanos enteros y no en forma de mermelada nos gusto.  Cocina espanola  Puntuacion: 9/10 Precio medio por persona: 25EUR Carrer d'Enric Alzamora, 3. This morning we could breath. The air was cool and  fresh but once again we were fooled .  This afternoon the sun is a ball of orange and then it disappeared as the smoke rolled in again.  I think of masks, for smoke and coronavirus. Our gardens can't breath. They need to adapt or die.  Drawing this afternoon I remembered a Shaun Tan book I gave the kids. It was about a big brother looking after his little brother as the world they lived in became stranger and stranger.  The headdress developed  by the little boy  seems like a new mask that we might wear, developed as we run out of paper masks ~ adaptation or die. Chesnok... kak pravil'no ego prinimat'?  Nadavno na moi Gastronomicheskii tur priekhala karasivitsa i bloger Polina ee zamechatel'nyi muzh Sasha.  Vgostiakh u zamechatel'nogo proizvoditelia vkusneishei kolbasy, uvidev golovki chesnoka sprashivaet: <<Kitaiskii?>>. Ia rassmeialas' i govoriu: << otkuda zhe v p'emontskii derevne kitaiskii chesnok?>>. >>Khoziain sam vyrastil svoi chesnok>>. No ia poniala, chto v Rossii okazyvaetsia naiti normal'nyi chesnok eto real'naia problema!  Ne mozhet byt', chtoby v strane s beskrainimi poliami iz chernozema, za kotoryi my platim v Italii ogromnye den'gi, pokupaia paket v supermarkete ili magazine tsvetov, byl ne v sostoianii s strane, gde prozhivanie 50% naseleniia Italii vystavit' normal'nyi chesnok. Mozhet my oblenilis' ili razuchilis' rabotat'?  Ia vot posadila na svoei minigriadke chesnok i sama budu ego vyrashchivat'!  I skazhu NET chuzhezemnomu chesnoku!  Ot chego i dlia chego on nuzhen nashemu organizmu, v tom chisle s dobavleniem meda?  Priem chesnoka na golodnyi zheludok okazyvaet sleduiushchuiu pol'zu: . . . Pomogaet ukrepit' immunitet. Reguliarnoe upotreblenie chesnoka pomogaet organizmu v bor'be s prostudoi i grippom, chto nemalovazhno. . . . Pomogaet v bor'be s opasnymi bakteriiami. Fitonitsidy, soderzhashchiesia v ovoshche, unichtozhaiut ne tol'ko bakterii i virusy, no i vozbuditelei infektsionnykh zabolevanii: kholery, tifa i t.d. . Ustraniaet problemy s pishchevareniem. Upotreblenie chesnoka predotvratit zabolevaniia kishechnika. . Ochishchenie organizma. Chesnok schitaetsia odnim iz luchshikh sredstv dlia vyvedeniia toksinov iz organizma. . . Sposobstvuet snizheniiu arterial'nogo davleniia. . Ne vse znaiut, chto upotreblenie ovoshcha privodit k rasshireniiu sosudov, vsledstvie chego snizhaetsia davlenie. Chesnok rekomendovan liudiam, stradaiushchim bolezniami legkikh i bronkhov. Iavliaetsia otlichnym antiseptikom, snimaet raznogo roda vospaleniia. . Pomogaet pri zabolevaniiakh sustavov. Blagotvornoe deistvie chesnoka na khriashchevuiu tkan' pomogaet pri bor'be s artrozom i artritom.  Slovom- chudo lekarstvo etot ovoshch. . Podpisyvaisia i podelites' s tem kto khochet byt' zdorovym! A short film done by the Film & TV faculty students at Oakfields College (including one Musical Theatre & Dance student). The story entails the hardships and aftermath of a catastrophic famine that hit the earth in the future. Elisa seeks to have her memory removed to forget all the horrendous memories of survival and her mother's death. Until an old wise man, Rodger, advises her that remembering is a good thing and crucial for the shaping of tomorrow's world. I met some people who struggles with depression&anxiety and they see medications as miracle. As people get to know more about the antidepressants,they started to think that those medication will suddenly make them happy. Medications only would not solve our all problems. We need to make changes in our life aswell. This is a post referring to that. Since I post this I get many disrespectful comments. Some people appatemtly thought that I know nothing about mental health and some people need to use pills. I take medications for 8 years and I am a senior psychology major. Of course I know how important to take meds but that's what I meant by that post. Sorry about the confusion guys but although we NEED to take meds in order to be happy-by making changes in our lives and changing our perspective WE GET BETTER. I promise. We can both take meds and make changes. Meds only won't be good for us. I hope it's clear now. Vas a volar en los proximos dias?  Aca te dejamos algunos consejos para cuando te dirijas al aeropuerto.  La seguridad aeroportuaria en todo el mumdo a mejorado sus sistemas de seguridad en los ultimos anos.  En especial despues de los atentados a las #torresgemelas  1. Una de las principales novedades despues del 9 de septiembre es que ninguna maleta viaja sin su pasajero. Es decir que no puedes enviar solo la maleta.  2. Viaja con zapatos comodos y facil de quitar para cuando debas pasar por los rayos x no pierdas tiempo.  3. Viaja con ropa comoda, sin tantas prendas, para que tu paso por rayos x puedas hacerlo rapidamente.  4. No tienes que llevar todas tus joyas puestas cuando vas a abordar. Quitartelas y guardarlas te hace perfer tiempo. No tienes que impresionar a nadie en aeropuerto. Guardalas para cuando llegues a tu destino.  5. Recuerda que en tu equipaje de mano no debes llevar objetos punzopenetrantes. Cortaunas, navajas, tijeras, agujas de tejer no deberias llevarla en el equipaje de mano.  6. Algunos paises tienen un tope de dinero en efectivo que puedes ingresar o retirar. Verifica esa informacion antes de llevar cantidades importantes de dinero. Si debes llevar mas dinero del tope, solo debes declrarlo y lo puedes llevar sin problemas.  7. Recuerda llegar 4 horad antes para tu chequeo. Recuerda que si es un vuelo internacional los oficiales de aduana o migracion pudieran hacer chequeos especiales, esto puede hacerte perder el vuelo y no seria responsabilidad de la aerolinea.  Toma en cuenta estas recomendaciones para tu proximo viaje.  #viajar #vida #avion #aeropuertos #pasajerosvip #volar #seguridad #segurosdeviaje #newyork #choroni

Ada beberapa tips pencegahan yang bisa dilakukan, yaitu:  Tutup mulut dan hidung ketika bersin  Hindari konsumsi makanan mentah dan tidak matang  Rutin mencuci tangan dengan sabun, atau cairan pembersih tangan  Hindari kontak dengan orang yang tidak sehat, atau menunjukkan gejala sakit  Hindari kontak fisik dengan hewan yang kurang bersih  Menjaga daya tahan tubuh, dengan memenuhi kebutuhan Vitamin C setiap hari  Penuhi kebutuhan nutrisi tubuh agar fungsi tubuh berjalan sempurna, dan daya tahan tubuh tetap kuat. Pigeon Pose  Targets: Glute Max, Glute Medius, Hip Flexors & Adductors  Equipment: Bodyweight  Difficulty: High Duration: 5-10 seconds for maintenance 30-60 seconds for improving muscle length  Application: This is a great stretch for opening the hips and releasing tension through the lower back. It targets both the glutes, adductors and the hip flexors.  Top Tip: Tuck your pelvis in by contracting your glutes to extend the hip flexor stretch.  Once in position continually slide your extended leg backwards and towards your torso to extend the stretch in your adductors and Glute Medius.  For a tutorial check out this link to our YouTube channel:

Kneeling Adductor Stretch  Targets: Adductors Equipment: Bodyweight  Difficulty: Low-Medium Duration: 5-10 seconds for maintenance 30-60 seconds for improving muscle length  Application: This is a great stretch for opening up the hips, stretching the internal rotators (adductors). Best used either post workout or on a recovery day.  Top Tip: Suck your belly button into your spine and tighten your core in order to flatten your back, this will increase your effectiveness of the stretch.  Speed your knees as wide apart as possible, keeping your ankles in line with your knees to extend the stretch.  For a tutorial check out this link to our YouTube channel:

Shoulder Dislocations  Targets: Pectorals, Deltoids, Rotator Cuffs & Biceps Equipment: Dowel/Broom Handle  Difficulty: Medium Duration: 5-15 repetitions used as a mobility warm up exercise  Application: A very effective way of both lengthening the muscles involved in movement of the shoulder joint and stimulating blood flow to this area.  Top Tip: If you struggle to get a full range of movement using a dowel, try using a theta and instead as it will allow a great range of motion without requiring the same level of mobility.  Keep your arm straight throughout, don't be tempted to bent your elbows to allow your arms to travel further over.  For a tutorial check out this link to our YouTube channel:

Face Up Lying Quad Stretch  Targets: Quadriceps, Hip Flexors & Tibialis Anterior  Equipment: Bodyweight  Difficulty: High Duration: 5-10 seconds for maintenance 30-60 seconds for improving muscle length  Application: This is a great stretch for targeting both the quadriceps and the hip flexors either post workout or on a recovery day.  Top Tip: Use a box behind you to rest your hands on if you struggle to lower yourself down far enough to feel the stretch.  Squeeze your glutes and tuck your hips in with your laces face down into the flow in order to maximise the effectiveness of the stretch whilst reducing the chances of the stretch going into your lumbar spine.  For a tutorial check out this link to our YouTube channel:

External Rotation  Targets: Rotator Cuffs Equipment: Theraband  Difficulty: Low-Medium Duration: 5-15 repetitions depending on degree of difficulty  Application: An exercise to assist in shoulder stabilisation and postural position as it strengthens the muscles that help to hold the shoulder girdle in correct position.  Top Tip: Ensure that your palms staying facing up toward the ceiling throughout, and be careful not to arch your back as this will change your position and change the muscles that you are using.  Keep your shoulders down and back with your core tight, whilst keeping your elbows pinned to your sides.  For a tutorial check out this link to our YouTube channel:

Seated Straight Leg Adductor Stretch  Targets: Adductors Equipment: Bodyweight  Difficulty: Low-Medium Duration: 5-10 seconds for maintenance 30-60 seconds for improving muscle length  Application: This is a great stretch for opening up the hips, stretching the internal rotators (adductors). Best used either post workout or on a recovery day.  Top Tip: Externally rotate your feet (away from the centre of your body) and lean forward into the stretch. Take deep breathes and increase the stretch as you exhale.  Speed your feet as wide apart as possible, keeping your knees straight. Lean forward and then side to side holding in each position. #Repost @draluizamallmann with @get_repost  Como prevenir o coronavirus?  O Ministerio da Saude orienta cuidados basicos para reduzir o risco geral de contrair ou transmitir infeccoes respiratorias agudas, incluindo o coronavirus. Entre as medidas estao:  Lavar as maos frequentemente com agua e sabonete por pelo menos 20 segundos, respeitando os 5 momentos de higienizacao. Se nao houver agua e sabonete, usar um desinfetante para as maos a base de alcool. Evitar tocar nos olhos, nariz e boca com as maos nao lavadas. Evitar contato proximo com pessoas doentes. Ficar em casa quando estiver doente. Cobrir boca e nariz ao tossir ou espirrar com um lenco de papel e jogar no lixo. Limpar e desinfetar objetos e superficies tocados com frequencia. Profissionais de saude devem utilizar medidas de precaucao padrao, de contato e de goticulas (mascara cirurgica, luvas, avental nao esteril e oculos de protecao). Para a realizacao de procedimentos que gerem aerossolizacao de secrecoes respiratorias como intubacao, aspiracao de vias aereas ou inducao de escarro, devera ser utilizado precaucao por aerossois, com uso de mascara N95.  #coronavirus #brasil #portoalegre #saude #health #virus #covid19 #coronavirus #covid_19

Novel Coronavirus Response Update  In line with the Government's activation of Dorscon level to Orange and in consideration of the safety and wellness of our visitors and church members, 3:16 Church will be putting in the following measures:  1. Temperature Taking Temperature taking will be conducted at our worship services and children ministry.  Members exhibiting the following symptoms should stay at home and/or seek medical attention. We will be unable to permit entry to those with these symptoms:  fever  running nose  teary eyes  cough  shortness of breath  2. Hand sanitation Hand sanitizers will be made available at the following places: (1) level 9, just outside the lift lobby (2) entrance of Big Picture (3) Children's Ministry registration table  3. Exchange of greetings Greetings should be exchanged with appropriate non-touch/contact gestures in consideration for each other's well-being. Wash hands frequently and avoid touching the face where possible.  4. In view of the nature of the viral transmission, we also request that those who have returned from China within the last 14-days to refrain from attending church gatherings (including services, cell meetings, and other group activities) for the moment. We may also be collecting information for contact tracing purposes.  I understand that these precautionary measures may put some of you at some inconvenience but they are necessary for the well-being of our community.  And having done all, we place our trust and hope in God. This is a time to draw even closer to our Lord JESUS CHRIST and seek His face. Let's all dwell in the shelter of the Most High and rest in the shadows of the Almighty.  See you later, 3:16 Fam! #coronavirus #covid_19 #prayforsg

TIRA O PE DA JACA E CAI NA PIZZA FIT!  Receitinha da Herbachef Marina Prado : Massa: - 1 cabeca de couve-flor (570 g); - 1 ovo; -  1/2  pacote de queijo parmesao ralado (50 g); - 1 sache de Sopa Instantanea Herbalife Nutrition sabor Frango com Legumes (28 g); - sal,  pimenta do reino, oregano a gosto; - oleo de coco ou azeite (para untar). Recheio: - 80 g de queijo mucarela ralado; -  1/2  cebola cortada em rodelas (opcional); - 50 g de requeijao light; - oregano a gosto.  Modo de preparo:  Bata a couve-flor no processador. Passe para uma tigela e leve ao micro-ondas por 1 minuto e meio. Deixe esfriar. Acrescente o ovo, o queijo ralado, a Sopa Instantanea Herbalife Nutrition sabor Frango com Legumes e tempere com o sal, a pimenta e o oregano. Unte uma forma de pizza com azeite ou oleo de coco e espalhe a massa em uma forma de pizza de 30 cm de diametro. Leve ao forno pre-aquecido a 180o C por 20 minutos ou ate as bordas dourarem. Retire o recheio com o queijo, a cebola, o requeijao e o oregano. Leve ao forno novamente ate o queijo derreter e sirva em seguida.  Experimenta e me conta depois! Escolha um grupo de palavras-chave relacionadas ao produto / servico que deseja anunciar, elabore um anuncio, defina o site para onde esses anuncios serao direcionados e pronto. Mais para a frente, quando sentir a necessidade de ter um maior controle sobre a sua conta, passe para a edicao completa.  Google Ads e a plataforma de anuncios e principal fonte de receita do Google. CARNAVAL? Periodo anual de festas profanas, originadas na Antiguidade e recuperadas pelo cristianismo, e que comecava no dia de Reis (Epifania) e acabava na Quarta-Feira de Cinzas, as vesperas da Quaresma [Festejos populares provenientes de ritos e costumes pagaos, caracterizavam-se pela liberdade de expressao e movimento. . .  Quem me acompanha nos stories sabe do que to falando...a questao nao e aproveitar todo esse festejo que significa: O primeiro elemento vem do latim caro, carnis (=carne), e o segundo elemento vem do verbo latino levare (=tirar, sustar, afastar). Ha quem suponha que a segunda parte do vocabulo pertenca ao dominio popular, do latim vale (=adeus); dai carnevale (=adeus a carne). . . Resta uma duvida: sera que e por isso que a "carne" e tao valorizada durante o carnaval? E sim aproveitar com mente no presente. . . Poznakom'tes' s eshchio odnim moim ekzoticheskim favoritom   Eto Chompu/ Rozovoe iabloko ili Malabarskaia sliva. Frukt obladaet ochen' liogkim (malovyrazhennym) vkusom i aromatom. No zato ochen' sochnyi i otlichno  utoliaet zhazhdu!  Frukt mozhno est' tselikom! net neobkhodimosti udaliat' shkurku ili kostochki.  Ne imeet protivopokazanii (za iskliucheniem individual'noi neperenosimosti)  Obladaet liogkim khvoinym privkusom.  Blizhe k kozhurke plod khrustiashchii i sochnyi, blizhe k seredine bolee miagkii i vatnyi.  Chompu -- eto nezamenimyi pomoshchnik pri prostude.  On toniziruet, snizhaet temperaturu, blagodaria mochegonnomu effektu otlichno vyvodit iz organizma toksiny.  Frukt imeet antibakterial'nye svoistva, chto pomogaet v bor'be s prichinami zabolevaniia. Piure iz frukta rekomenduetsia davat' detiam vo vremia puteshestvii dlia ukrepleniia immuniteta i profilaktiki ORVI.  Reguliarnoe upotreblenie rozovogo iabloka normalizuet rabotu zheludochno- kishechnogo trakta, pomogaet pishchevareniiu, uluchshaet metabolizm. Blagodaria kompleksu vitaminov i mineralov uluchshaetsia sostoianie kozhi i volos, propadaiut priznaki gipertonii na rannei stadii, i ukhodit otechnost'.  Edinstvennyi minus on zhe prichina pochemu ego pochti ne vstretish' na prilavkakh stran gde on ne kul'tiviruetsia - eto korotkii srok khraneniia!  Luchshe vsego frukt upotrebliat' v tot zhe den' chto vy ego kupili. Maksimum na sleduiushchii den' (esli khotite v kholodil'nike). No poprobovat' ego stoit odnoznachno!  A vy probovali Chompu?  kakoi ona vam pokazalas' na vkus? kto-to govorit chto u neio est' tsvetochnyi privkus... ia ne zametila. . .

GADANIE NA VOSKE.  Chto segodnia mezhdu nami? Segodnia budet 2 varianta, 2 chashki. Vybiraite na ugad.  1 chashka: Vash Partner daleko ot Vas, vas razdeliaet rasstoianie. Na serdtse u nego tiazhelo, denezhnye problemy u nego, so zdorov'em problemy. Vozmozhno riadom s sem'ei on seichas. K vam u nego iskrennie chuvstva (serdtse vylilos'), stremitsia myslenno k Vam. No ob'ektivnye prichiny meshaiut priekhat'(vizhu gory). Uekhal on vnezapno, eto bylo bol'shim udarom dlia Vas, Vy zakrylis' ot nego, da i ot vsekh tozhe. Khochetsia pobyt' odnoi(odnomu) Vam. Na dushe tiazhelo (kamen'). Razobrat'sia v sebe khotite. Poetomu segodnia mezhdu Vami pauza. Partner priviazan k Vam, somnenii v etom net, a Vot u Vas somneniia na schiot Vashikh chuvstv. Ostyli kak budto, chuvstvuete. Budto oborvalas' sviaz'. No, eto vremennoe iavlenie, ne volnuites'. Prosto zima, prosto ustali. Poterpite do vesny.partner ispravit situatsiiu, popravit zdorov'e i verniotsia k Vam, vmeste s vesennim tioplom. Mesiatsa cherez 1,5-2.  2 chashka: Vash Partner ne svoboden. U nego obiazatel'stva pered drugim chelovekom. K vam on otnositsia kak k prazdniku (buket). S Vami legko i prazdnichno. U mnogikh proigraetsia - tainaia sviaz', kak liubovniki. Zhivet on v odnom s vami gorode, no dostatochno daleko, poetomu priezzhaet v gosti ne chasto. Zhdiote Vy partnera svoego postoianno ( znak beskonechnosti). Rugaetes' i snova mirites' (kacheli). Vot i nedavno Vy snova porugalis' i on ushiol. Molcha stradaete  uzhe neskol'ko dnei (sliozy). Otpustit' ne mozhete situatsiiu, a Partner ne pishet i ne zvonit (trubka telefonnaia). Utrite sliozy svoi, uspokoites'. Zaimites' soboi. Otvlekites'. Sam pridiot bukval'no segodnia-zavtra. Potomu, chto skuchaet sil'no (tianet ruki k vam). Vse budet khorosho, i snova po znaku beskonechnosti vse prodolzhitsia po prezhnemu. .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  #gadaniebesplatno #gadanieonlain #gadanie #gadanienavoske #vosk #voskresen'e #coronavirus #koronavirus #podpiskazapodpisku #laiktaim #laikivzaimno #sleduizamnoi #liketime #likeforlikes #likeforfollow #vzaimnyelaiki #vzaimnyepodpiski #laikzalaikvzaimno #piar #piarigra #piarbesplatno #vzaimnyipiar #sleduizamechtoi #sledui #dizain #polet #psikhologiiaotnoshenii #psikhologiialichnosti #liubov' #schast'e

Ya tenemos gobierno, pero el show no ha hecho mas que empezar. ***  Los partidos acusan de falta de autocritica a sus adversarios, los periodistas dicen que "para los politicos la autocritica es criticar al otro"... pero, ?la tiene el periodismo? ***  Se hacen los ofendiditos cuando no les invitan a una rueda de prensa, y repiten aquello de "somos los intermediarios entre la clase politica y el pueblo" pero el periodismo ha fracasado en esa mision. ***  La transparencia esta muy bien y es necesaria, pero cuando sabes que los invitados a la fiesta van a malmeter en lugar de informar... se te quitan las ganas. ***  En las tertulias mananeras te regalan su coctel de prejuicios con un chorrito de argumentario de partido y unos cubitos de encuestas heladas... ?pero leer cuarenta paginas y explicarlas a la gente? !Ni hablar que luego hay que poner la mano para cobrar! ***  Toda la mierda que tragaste estas navidades, y la que tragaras, toda esa crispacion y toxicidad... puedes ahorrartela leyendo el puto Pacto de Gobierno entre el PSOE y Unidas Podemos. Link en BIO. ***  En cuanto salio publicado me lei las primeras 10 paginas, y aunque aun no he podido terminarlo, me basto para comprobar que de cada seis "periodistas tertulianos", solo uno demostraba haberlo leido. ***  A veces algunos programas de variedades hacen mejor periodismo que muchos de presunto "analisis politico". ***  Vineta cedida por @J_R_Mora publicada el 3 de Abril de 2019 en @CTXT_es *** #Periodismo #Pacto #negociacion #gobierno #transparencia #calidad #analisis #polemica #periodistas #politica

Cuando te cuentan lo del "Pin Parental" te dicen los motivos de las familias y los partidos pero, ?y los derechos de los ninos? ***  No estamos hablando sobre el derecho a decidir las actividades extraescolares, que ya existe y funciona. El "Pin Parental" pretende ir mas alla. Se trata de cuando el derecho de los padres a "crear a sus hijos a su imagen y semejanza" va contra los derechos de los menores. Segun la agencia de noticias EFE: "la propuesta de VOX para que los padres den su consentimiento a actividades con contenidos morales o sexuales". ***  Art. 27.2 de la Constitucion: "La educacion tendra por objeto el pleno desarrollo de la personalidad humana en el respeto a los principios democraticos de convivencia y a los derechos y libertades fundamentales." ***  Hay una gran diferencia entre decidir sobre actividades que "solo" buscan ampliar el curriculum y aquellas orientadas a protegerlos. Las primeras son prescindibles, las segundas no. ***  Creo que los ninos tienen derecho a saber identificar, evitar y denunciar cualquier maltrato o abuso, aunque sus padres crean que en algunos casos esta bien maltratar. *** Creo que tambien tienen derecho a saber como evitar un contagio de Enfermedades de Transmision Sexual, aunque sus padres no quieran. ***  Hay muchos otros casos en los que si carece de formacion adecuada el nino puede correr peligro o poner en peligro a los demas. ***  El terreno familiar siempre estuvo abonado para que los discursos de odio y la indefension de la infancia se transmitan de unas generaciones a otras. ***  Pero como hay demasiadas noticias sobre sus consecuencias, el sistema educativo intenta dar pasos para evitarlo. Y claro, a algunos esto les agua la fiesta. ***  No por casualidad, la presidenta de VOX de Madrid ha sido investigada por un posible "delito de incitacion al odio" al celebrar un acto de campana electoral del 10N frente a un centro de menores en Sevilla. ***  El debate es mas facil si nos centramos en los derechos de la infancia. ***  Vineta de @j_r_mora publicada en @ctxt_es *** #PinParental #Educacion #infancia #ideologia #politica #vox #odio #constitucion #Solidaridad #Espana

Precaution virus outbreak:           Stay aware! Because being ignorant is not an option, Yes! We dont know what we dont know.. Yes,There are things we can't control.. But! also lots of things we know and we can control..           Nah yg kita bisa kontrol:           1. Berdoa dijauhkan dari segala macam virus, bakteri, penyakit, Amen           2. Boosting Immune  Pentingnya menjaga stamina keluarga kita (termasuk staff rumah tangga/PRT), selain makan 6 porsi buah, sayur organik, mentah dan minimal 5 macam warna: solusi menaikkan daya tahan tubuh ya, cari tambahan makanan / suplementasi vitamin yang baik,  seperti apa? Suplementasi organik (tanpa bahan kimia, tanpa pewarna) itu yang baik, yang bisa memenuhi kebutuhan vitamin dalam tubuh untuk meningkatkan daya tahan tubuh. Why? Karena kita melawan radikal bebas, dari zat karsinogen kita makan, polusi udara yang kita hirup  termasuk virus, bakteri, dan alergen yg tidak bisa kita lihat kasat mata           3.  Perbanyak asupan Protein, why? Karena asam amino di dalam kandungan protein, menciptkan T cell yang berguna sebagai armada tentara melawan virus, bakteri dalam tubuh (coba google in detail)           4. Stok hand Sanitizer, dan edukasi anak dan staff di rumah untuk rajin cuci tangan dengan sabun dan selalu bawa hand sanitizer di dalam tas.           5. Stok masker, selalu ada dalam tas. Dan harus di pakai jika kita dalam keadaan drop, (masker N95)           Para pakar menyatakan koronavirus bisa transmisi via udara, sambil menunggu WHO statement, Ada baiknya kita protek diri dan sadar diri jika sedang drop / sakit lebih baik di rumah saja, dan atau jika terpaksa pakai masker  6. Investasi Filter udara, Bijak berinvestasi air filter yg kerapatan hepa filter nya lebih kecil dr Virus Korona. Fyi, Virus korona besarnya 0.1 - 0.2 mikron. Jd cek spesifikasi air filter di rumah, apakah lebih kecil dari 0.1 mikron? Kalau tidak - ya cuma bisa filter debu saja..           7. Foto Swipe left : wise mom will think, apakah mau jadi kan paru sebagai filter udara, atau investasi filter udara? (After and before use) saya pilih hepa filter yang kerapatannya 0.0024 mikron (1000x lebih kecil dari virus korona)

O pulmao inala o ar puro - Qi do ar. Esse Qi (qing qi), se une ao Qi alimentar para formar o Qi peitoral. O Qi peitoral regula a inalacao e a exalacao ajuda o coracao a controlar o fluxo harmonioso do sangue para a periferia. .  O pulmao governa o Qi e controla a dispersao do Qi. Essa energia garantem que os liquidos que ascendem do baco se dispersem para a periferia. O pulmao controla a dispersao e a descida dos liquidos corporais. Tambem regula a passagem da agua. .  Na Medicina Chinesa, as desarmonias dos pulmoes estao inicialmente associados a tristeza, luto e depressao. Isto significa que manter-se nestes estados emocionais por longos periodos, pode afetar as capacidades dos pulmoes de desempenharem suas capacidades vitais. .  Os sintomas fisicos ainda podem desenvolver sintomas emocionais e virse versa. Na filosofia chinesa, a forca dos pulmoes esta ligada a coragem e a sinceridade. Pulmoes fracos podem estar associados a disturbios varios de respiracao, letargia e sintomas desarmoniosas de pele como eczema, erisipela e seborreia.  Indispensavel e movimentar-se para aquecer o pulmao! Rir tambem ajuda bastante! Faz o sangue circular junto com a respiracao! In May I became the first in my family to graduate with a master's degree. Had my great aunt Brenda "Auntie" not stepped up to raise other people's children, she would have been the first.                                        I asked Auntie what attending my graduation was like for her and here is her response.                                                                  The older I get, the more I understand and deeply appreciate the sacrifices she's made for our family. We rarely talk about how "aunties" and "grands" in families like mine & especially within Black and Brown communities are the foundation of the family and martyr for other people's dreams.                                        This is a song for auntie and all women like her. May we lift up her story, honor her experience, support her choices, and commit to ending the perpetual cycle of stifling her future too. The loss of #KobeBryant, #GiGi, and all involved in the accident and the loss of #NipseyHussle whose 1-year anniversary is upon us has me thinking constantly about how their families will recover from these horrendous series of events.                                                                               The reality, and what gives me hope, is that so many of us have some version of these unthinkable circumstances in our own family histories and that is why we can empathize so deeply with their families.                                                     Traumatic events and #generationalCurses do not have to define your family identity.                                                       The only way to get through it is to sit in the reality of the pain and pick up the pieces one by one in spite of the difficulty it takes to get through it. That's how healing is done. IO SONO SEMPRE STATO SINCERO NELLA MIA VITA! SEMPRE VASCONVOLTO! COME FRANCESCO, L'AMICO VOLATO VIA! ALMENO CHI E ONESTO NO! SE NON MI DATE POSSIBILITA DI DIMOSTRARE COME FACCIO? AVESSI USATO FACEBOOK, NON SAREBBE SUCCESSO! SAREBBE ANDATO TUTTO BENE!ORA MI PIANGE IL CUORE PER LA PERDITA CHE ABBIAMO AVUTO!E STATA TUTTA OPERA DI MAIOLO ORESTE! GLI AVEVO DETTO DI NON PERMETTERSI A CONTATTARVI, INVECE GIURANDO SUL PADRE MORTO DICEVA SIAMO GENTE D'ONORE,PER 3 VOLTE HO DETTO NON POSSO! AVEVA PORTATO DALLA SUA, SAPENDO LE ESIGENZE ECONOMICHE ANCHE IL BUON FRANCESCO,CHE ORA MI FA MALE PER I FIGLI,SEMPRE CON LUI!VASCO COME FACCIO SE NON CHIAMATE ME? O fator determinante para a superacao dos medos e a pratica, a vivencia daquilo que nos amedronta. Absoliutno kazhdomu zdravomysliashchemu cheloveku, nabliudaiushchemu za vektorom dvizheniia COVID-19, s fevralia poniatno, chto i v Rossii budet epidemiia, karantin, krizis i vse iz nego vytekaiushchie. No mir polon durakov, kotorye dumaiut, chto imenno ikh eto ne kosnetsia. Oni prodolzhaiut letat' za granitsu, a vernuvshis' v Rossiiu ne sobliudaiut nikakikh mer po samoizoliatsii. Rossiia nachinaet medlenno pokryvat'sia koronavirusom. Neozhidanno? Net, logichno. Bol'shinstvo po-prezhnemu ne prinimaet nadvigaiushchuiusia ugrozu vser'ez. Schitaiut, poka net signala sverkhu, vse khorosho. Signal budet, cherez nedeliu-dve vy uvidite novuiu real'nost', pod nazvaniem "vserossiskii karantin". Khochetsia verit' chto vlast' tak zhe primet i drugie neobkhodimye mery, vvedet riad ogranichenii, primet aktual'nye popravki v zakon, opredelit finansovye, nalogovye, kreditnye i prochie poslableniia. No ne zhdite ukazanii sverkhu, deistvuite priamo seichas. Samoizoliatsiia - luchshii vykhod. Sozdaite finansovuiu podushku, zapasites' vprok edoi, vodoi, antiseptikami, maskami, neobkhodimymi vam lekarstvami i zheleznym terpeniem. Deistvuite raschetlivo, s kholodnoi golovoi. Ne panikuite, a gotov'tes' naslazhdat'sia obshchestvom blizkikh i dorogikh liudei, interesnymi fil'mami, igrami, knigami, vkusnoi edoi i drugimi ne menee priiatnymi zaniatiiami, na kotorykh v obychnoi povsednevnoi zhizni, mnogim iz vas, nikogda ne khvataet vremeni. Poimite, esli vy ne virusolog, to nichego luchshe prostoi samoizoliatsii vy sdelat' ne mozhete. Svedite na minimum priamye kontakty s vneshnim mirom. Otnosites' otvetstvenno ko vsem meram profilaktiki. Ne peregruzhaite meditsinskuiu sistemu. Chem men'she infitsirovannykh, tem vyshe u nikh shans poluchit' polnuiu kompleksnuiu terapiiu i vyzhit'. Zhdite spada pandemii i vaktsinu. Griadet vremia bol'shikh peremen, pereosmysleniia i peretasovki zhiznennykh prioritetov. i'm well, staying home at this yugoslavian apartment. thanks for writing, sorry i'm bad with a timely response. some plans changed due to #coronavirus, yes, but who am i complain - lucky to have a job, place to live, people to love. and a remote working is not new to me (nor it is exciting to go back to)  trying to focus on what i've got instead of what i don't. to be honest, can't think of a better place to be in times like this - belgrade is very walkable/runnable. as a former capital to a huge socialist state, city is well designed for communities: despite their income or area residents have an access to dozens of green spaces (parks, miniforests, nature reserves), public spaces for sport. the megapolis is not that crowded, so if a park has 5 runners and 2 sitting on bench, u can go the next one 10 minutes away and a probability of having safe 7 meters to urself is pretty high.  i spent last summer here, and it can't compete with a spring. spring is blooming, spring is warm and windy. spring has no mosquitoes!  i may not have the longest relationship with this city as with some others. but i've known its story, lines, colors, smells, sounds from somewhere. maybe from books & movies, or as a kid born to a communist state and raised on its ashes, i get serbia's spirit, tears, joy, its charm and its capital's shades of grey. its language is a mix of my two native languages (slavic & turkic) with a laid-back temper. laid back is what i'd like to learn  #centralasianontheroad #serbia #srbija #coronavirus #beograd #belgrade #stayhome

Podra parecer visualmente incomoda por sus infinitas asociaciones con la enfermedad, venenos y sobre todo la muerte, y mas aun con todo el escepticismo que gira en torno al coronavirus,  pero lo cierto  es que esta obra es  realizada con fines instructivos y por lo otro, estoy tranquilo y mi hogar tambien pues la promesa de nuestro Dios establece que, y cito: "Ninguna  plaga tocara nuestra morada..."   Creyendo eso es facil tener paz en la tormenta. . . . . Continuando con el tema, a la hora de realizar un retrato es necesario conocer la estructura craneal y los elementos que le otorgan su forma caracteristica, tales como: El hueso frontal, cuencas de los ojos, hueso del pomulo, maxilar, mandibula, parietal, occipital, temporal entre otros. . . . Tener una clara comprension de ellos a la hora de realizar un rostro nos ayudara a que al momento de agregar los elementos de la cara todo quede proporcionado y en su sitio dando un aspecto natural a la imagen  . . . . Me and my fiance are blessed. We live with his family on the east coast. I left my Californian apartment a few weeks short of the end of my lease to move in. We have only left the house for a walk around the neighborhood in the nine days we've been inside. We're taking advantage of the world on fire. Everyday we exercise the muscles we've always wanted bigger or more toned. We read the books that have been sitting on our shelves. We watch the movies in our Netflix lists. We cook and clean and stick to our skin care routine. We realize we are lucky and want to extend our gratitude to those who are still working, or living under extreme circumstances during this collectively traumatic experience. Please stay safe, give where you can, and stay inside! !![?]Ostorozhno, longrid!![?] [?][?]17 marta UEFA oglasil verdikt - chempionat Evropy 2020 perenositsia na god v sviazi s koronavirusom. Reshenie prognoziruemoe i logichnoe, no gorech' razocharovaniia prisutstvuet. Ne tak davno mne udalos' kupit' bilety na match Evro-2020 Ukraina - Avstriia, kotoryi dolzhen byl sostoiatsia v iiune v Bukhareste. Teper' realizatsiia planov perenositsia na god. Konechno eto meloch' na fone proiskhodiashchego. No vse zhe khochu otmetit' sleduiushchee... [?][?]Ia ni kapli ne virusolog, sovsem ne vrach i voobshche chelovek, s meditsinoi imeiushchii ves'ma daliokie otnosheniia. Bolee togo, ia mogu okazat'sia otkrovennym gluptsom i pozhalet' o skazannom. Tem ne menee vot moi 5 kopeek otnositel'no koronavirusa. Ia ne govoriu, chto COVID-19 - eto pustiak. Chto ot informatsii o nem stoit otmakhivat'sia kak ot nazoilivoi mukhi. Khochu skazat' tol'ko odno: ne vosprinimaite vsio na veru i pomen'she vpityvaite novosti o koronaviruse, kotorye lezut k nam iz kazhdogo chainika - zdorovee budete, kak minimum psikhicheski. Esli chemu i nauchil menia Institut zhurnalistiki sovmestno s rabotoi v SMI, a takzhe prosto zhiznennyi opyt, tak eto tomu, chto verit' ne stoit nikomu. Ili korrektnee - nuzhno kriticheski vosprinimat' liubuiu informatsiiu, popadaiushchuiu v mozg. I ne vazhno, avtoritetnaia li eto programma na TV, populiarnyi sait v intrenete ili slova blizkogo druga, lichno znakomogo s chelovekom, rodstvennik kotorogo sobstvennymi glazami videl koronavirus. [?]Za poslednie dni "poschastlivilos'" naslushat'sia takogo breda, kotoryi adekvatnomu i dumaiushchemu cheloveku na golovu ne nalezet. Poniatno, vo mnogom vinoi tomu panika, kotoraia otkliuchaet mozg.  No ved' zachastuiu etu paniku porozhdaem my sami, bezdumno retransliruia musor, kotoryi sypletsia so vsekh storon.  i[?]Ne zabyvaite ne tol'ko pogloshchat' informatsiiu, no i zadeistvovat' seroe veshchestvo v rezhime obrabotki i analiza onoi. Moite ruki, pomnite o profilaktike, zabot'tes' o sebe i blizkikh. Kak by ni kazalos', chto apokalipsis blizko, pover'te, vsio budet khorosho!  PS Odna iz liubimykh tsitat. "17 mgnovenii vesny", Miuller: "Verit' v nashe vremia nel'zia nikomu. Poroi dazhe samomu sebe. Mne - mozhno!" PPS Pobezhal zakupat'sia grechkoi, vodkoi, i tualetnoi bumagoi

I am currently witnessing a congressional hearing about the airline passenger experience.  Flying is much more difficult to tolerate than it once was, (i am not referring to TSA or airport operations) and the airline side is defending the slippage of standards.  Congresspeople are pointing out the worsening conditions, the unquestionable insanity of fees charged by airlines, the fact that the airlines continue to raise the fees, and the apathy of the airlines toward their customers.  The representatives from the airlines are stating that this is all okay.  AND FEES?  I almost can't believe the level of vacuous drivel that is flowing out of the airline side.  Guess what-checked baggage and fees for reservation changes generated billions of dollars in 2019. And airlines cry every couple of years, about looming bankruptcy.  One representative is apparently trying to say that one airline's core business comes from people who don't carry luggage, and have no desire to select seats.  One of these dips just said out loud that as far as he is concerned, passengers basically cannot get Covid-19 from other passengers on a plane!!! And WOW! Aqui em Goias, de acordo com o decreto de ontem do governador, a partir de amanha fecharemos por 15 dias pra contribuir com a prevencao do COVID-19.  Agora e o momento de pensarmos na sua saude e, quando tudo isso passar, a gente volta a se ver.   Enquanto isso, vamos preparar combos de tratamento pra comprarem agora e fazer depois. E kits de tratamento pra vc continuar se cuidando em casa. Caso precisem, faremos entregas sem custo adicional durante esse periodo.

Non sappiamo come allenarci in questo periodo? Vi lascio dieci esercizi che potete fare con un cuscino, un bastone di una scopa e una sedia! 1) quadrupedia, porto il ginocchio verso l'esterno. Per 3 volte 10 aperture per gamba e tengo 1" 2) squat su una gamba, mi aiuto con una sedia per scendere. 4 serie da 8 ripetizioni 3) pike press. Se fosse troppo difficile fatelo appoggiati al muro 3 serie da 12 ripetizioni 4) split squat. Rimango dritto sia nella discesa che nella salita. Ginocchio ad altezza del tallone della gamba avanti. 4 serie da 15 ripetizioni per gamba 5) push down. Gomiti distesi, per salire spingo in basso le mani contro la sedia.  4 serie da 10 ripetizioni 6) posizione pistol squat estendo la gamba avanti, di lato e dietro  4 serie da 8 cambi gamba 7) deadlift a una gamba sola 4 serie da 8 ripetizioni 8) quadrupedia, ginocchia sollevate tocco la sedia con la mano.  3 serie da 12 ripetizioni 9) bridge con appoggio le scapole alla sedia/materasso/divano, porto il ginocchio al petto 3 serie da 20 ripetizioni alternando le gambe. 10) in piedi, ginocchio al petto e alzo il braccio dello stesso lato 3 serie da 12 ripetizioni per gamba  Sfidiamoci usando l'instabilita, proviamoci e sbagliamo insieme!  Sbagliamo. Impariamo. Miglioriamo!  C.M.  #crossfit #allenamento #allungamento #climbing #arrampicata #hometraining #healthy #corpolibero #coronavirus

Se abbiamo dei semplici elastici o dei piccoli pesi come una cassa d'acqua, possiamo usarli per fare dei lavori molto vari. Vi lascio 9 esercizi che possono sfidarvi: 1) goblet squat 1/2 + 1 - 5 serie da 8 ripetizioni 2) rematore con elastico, 3 serie x 12 ripetizioni, velocita lenta 3) bridge + leg curl, 4 serie 20 ripetizioni alternando le gambe 4) superset, ovvero nessuna pausa tra i due esercizi, reverse fly + alzata laterale 3 serie da 8 ripetizioni x esercizio ( 8+8) 5) rematore con due pesi in posizione di affondo, 3 serie da 6 ripetizioni x gamba 6) split squat, peso sopra la testa, 3" in discesa e salita. 5 serie x 10 ripetizioni alternando le gambe 7) stacco rumeno, 1" di fermo nel punto piu profondo, 3 serie da 12 ripetizioni 8) superset, curl bicipiti + French press in piedi, 3 serie da 12+8. Fermo di 1" nel curl bicipiti sia in discesa che in salita con gomito a 90deg 9) superset, tirata al mento mani altezza spalle + mani altezza mento, 3 serie da 8+8  Provate a svolgere questi esercizi in modo lento e controllato in ogni angolo  Sbagliamo. La frase del #streetart de la foto, lleva alli mas de 30 anos!  Pasaron muchas manos de pintura, pero la frase sigue alli. .  La primera vez que la vi fue un marzo de 1989. Iba caminando a la Facultad de Ingenieria con mas incertidumbres que certezas y con mas miedo que alegria, recien llegado a #Montevideo. .  La recuerdo como un #graffiti hecho con spray, como muchos graffitis de esa epoca post dictadura y en medio de un plebiscito para derogar una ley de amnistia a los militares acusados de violar derechos humanos. .  Ver la frase me sorprendio. El mensaje no era politico, era para el alma. .  Cada vez que pasaba esperaba que no la borraran o que no le pegaran propaganda arriba. Eran epocas en las que las paredes de las casas estaba escritas o con pegatinas, muy distinto a estos tiempos. .  Un dia aparecio pintada la fachada pero con el graffiti repintado! Que alegria!!! Seguramente la gente del hogar estudiantil que funciona (o funcionaba) en ese lugar tomaron la frase como parte de la casa. Les generaria el coraje y valor necesario para afrontar cada dia tambien! .  Una de mis hijas que estudia ingenieria, tambien la busca desde el omnibus cuando pasa, siente lo mismo. .  Hace meses que queria hacer este post, mostrando la foto y mi historia con esta casa. La foto la saque en febrero un dia que ibamos con mi hijo a pescar. Ni en ese momento, ni cuando pensaba hacer el post se me hubiera ocurrido que fuera tan oportuno publicarlo! .  De corazon les deseo que la frase les de animo y esperanza como a nosotros. Por algo esas letras permanecen alli con cada vez mas arte!  La ubicacion es Bulevard Espana esq. J. Paullier #Montevideo #Uruguay . .  Animo companer@s! En esta epoca la salud es lo primero. Quedate en casa no solo para cuidarte, sino tambien para cuidar a los demas. A su vez es importante no descuidar la salud mental, mi consejo es que aproveches cualquier espacio de luz solar para poder despejarte y no sentir tanto el encierro. Es por ese motivo, que decidi hacer home office a la luz del sol, rodeada de las plantas, para poder estar en contacto con lo mas cercano que tengo en mi casa de la naturaleza. Tambien es recomendable no quedarse en pijama, hacer ejercicio regularmente, comer de manera saludable manteniendose hidratados y tratar de alternar las noticias con comedias, para que sea mas llevadero el dia a dia. Se que es dificil estar en cuarentena, pero esto es una pandemia, y al quedarnos en casa no solo nos estamos cuidando, sino que tambien estamos ayudando a que no se siga propagando. Sebelum lahir virus covid-19 itu ada virus flu burung dan virus flu babi. Bukankah para pemakan daging ayam dan babipun masih ada hingga sekarang dan mereka semua baik-baik saja. Malah jauh dari itu ada virus HIV/Aids, kan?  Sebagian dari ODHA malah menikmati sisa hidupnya yang entah kapan akan tutup layar. Iya, usia itu siapa yang tahu. Bukankah itu berarti mereka bersyukur dengan cara menikmati itu semua.  Jauh lagi sebelum HIV, pastilah ada. Mungkin pada masa nenek moyang kita atau bahkan leluhur-leluhur kita. Tapi mereka tak pernah ditaklukkan oleh penyakit. Justru sebaliknya, mereka menaklukkan semua penyakit dengan cara yang unik.  Ayolah, kawan ... kita itu manusia yang tak mungkin jauh dari kata sosial. Setakut apa sih kita hadapi covid ini? Penyakit bukan untuk ditakuti tapi diwaspadai. Sebab, virus itu seperti penculik. Sekali kita lengah kita akan kehilangan harta yang kita miliki yaitu, tubuh.  Saya harap ini bermanfaat bagi kita. Cukup bermanfaat bukan dimanfaatkan!  Ingat, terlalu banyak yang mengetik sesuatu dengan berlebih maka kita lupa bagaimana menulis.  #database #covid #CoronaVirus #VirusCorona #HaloASEAN #HaloAsia

I hope you're all keeping well & staying safe. Life's so strange right now and extremely scary. Watching it all unfold and living through the uncertainty of what is going to happen next, not knowing when it is all going to be over, I have realised that how much of an impact every person has when we work alongside each other with empathy and kindness towards one another. -  If anything, COVID19 has taught us that there are so many temporary things in life, some of which we think our lives revolve around, work, gym, shopping, etc. and yet every day we are learning to live without them. -  Social media is doing an amazing job right now in terms of keeping us all connected and socialising throughout this difficult time, however, it can so easily consume us with negative thoughts. What we need is already what we have or what is available to us every single day. We don't need the next bigger, better, faster thing. It is all materialistic, and temporary, because what do we do with it all when we're having to isolate ourselves from the world? It all becomes meaningless. If you have love, you're already winning. - All of the Sundays that we've dreaded because Monday was soon approaching & we've got to go to work, turning down invitations to see people 'cause we wasn't in the mood, being able to walk in to a shop to buy basic food.. all of these things that we're currently unable to do for the foreseeable future, is now becoming apparent how much we should value what we have & how lucky we are to have it. - It is sad that something like this has to happen in order for us all to realise what the important things are in our lives & what truly is a necessity when it comes down to it. - When this has all blown over, of course, we'll meet our friends & family & go for a pint, a walk, to the shops, to a football game... but at least we will appreciate and be forever grateful for being able to do those things. I hope people start to focus on what we DO have in life & not what we DON'T have. For once in our lifetime, the whole world is focused on one thing & I hope throughout all of this, we will all learn one thing, that one thing being, GRATITUDE. The greatest wealth is health

El selenio juega es una pieza clave en la defensa  y proteccion contra enfermedades virales infecciosas y , obviamente, como prevencion y proteccion contra el coronavirus .  El selenio es un micronutriente que juega un rol importante en  la respuesta inmune, salud de la tiroides, prevencion del dano oxidativo , entre otras funciones . Cuando por medio de la alimentacion ingerimos selenio, este micronutriente,  a traves de una reaccion bioquimica, producira la selenocisteina en el organismo que luego sera incorporada a las selenioproteinas . Las selenioproteinas cumplen un rol VITAL en el equilibrio oxido-redutivo . Tienen propiedades antioxidantes como la Glutation Peroxidasa.  Los virus producen especies reactivas de oxigeno que son combatidas por el Glutation Peroxidasa para reducir la replicacion viral y mutacion del virus. Las selenioproteinas tuvieron que ser introducidas por la naturaleza posterior al codigo genetico, probablemente, debido a un grave estres oxidativo en el medio ambiente. Un grave estres oxidativo en el medio ambiente que ponia en peligro a la supervivencia de la biosfera, muchos miles de millones de anos antes de que apareciera la especia humana. El mismo problema de falta de selenio es compartido por toda la biosfera desde los mamiferos hasta la bacteria .  Por ello, la deficiencia de selenio es un problemas ecologico sumamente grave. La deficiencia de selenio produce gran nivel de estres oxidativo que hace mutar al virus y asi,  podra infectar a otras especies , lo que en condiciones normales no aconteceria . La deficiencia de selenio puede causar enfermedades como la miocardiopatia de Keshan, en la cual se descubrio que el problema no era el virus sino la falta de selenio . Llama la atencion el dato de que toda la poblacion europea este con deficiencia de selenio y mas aun cuando se observa que un gran porcentaje de muertes por coronavirus son por shock cardiogenico . Infelizmente, los suelos actualmente estan devastados de selenio. Por eso, los vegetales ya no tienen selenio para proveer al resto de la biosfera a traves de la cadena alimentaria. CONFINEMENT J-6  . ... si longtemps que je n'ai pas poste ! ... . Alors les loulous, vous etes en train de devenir fous ? Ou ca chille tranquille devant les livres, Netflix et les reseaux sociaux ?  . Pour ma part, confinement ou pas, je suis enfermee dans mon appart pour me creer un petit nid douillet, car mon chez moi, c'est aussi mon lieu de travail : double raison de m'y sentir bien vu le temps que j'y passe...  . Aujourd'hui, j'entame le 12eme jour de travaux, et j'ai un jardin pour prendre quelques bains de soleil entre deux coups de pinceaux [?] . Cela dit, j'ai hate d'en avoir fini, parce que c'est complique de se doucher au milieu des rouleaux et de cuisiner parmi des dizaines d'eponges. Et je craque de partout, je suis completement cassee !  . J'ai hate de vous montrer le resultat aussi ! Ce sera l'occasion de vous faire un petit tour d'horizon de mon lieu de vie.  . Meme si c'est dur d'etre coupe de tout, je pense que ce confinement est plus que necessaire. J'avoue ne pas avoir pris tres au serieux ce virus dans ses 1ers balbutiements, mais j'ai revu mon jugement - en meme temps, comment ne pas le revoir ? On est assez mal barres en Alsace, en plus !  . Mais j'ai aussi envie de voir le positif dans tout ca, car il y en a ! La planete, enfin, recommence a respirer.  Je pense qu'il faudra en tirer des lecons, une fois l'epidemie passee !  Qu'on prenne conscience de notre maniere de vivre et qu'on la revoit ! Nous avons besoin de la Terre, mais elle n'a pas besoin de nous... Elle nous le prouve bien en ces temps troubles... Et il etait grand temps qu'on l'ecoute ! . Donnez-moi un peu de vos nouvelles, les loulous ! . #[?]Comment vous portez-vous ? Vous allez bien ? Vos proches aussi ? . #[?]Et comment se passe votre confinement ? Comment vous occupez-vous ? . Je vous embrasse tous (de loin) [?] .  by @lphotographie68 qui me manque

Os primeiros casos de coronavirus humanos foram isolados em 1937, porem so em 1965 recebeu esse nome, devido a semelhanca com uma coroa ao serem obervados atraves do microscopio. O virus e subdividido em 7 tipos: Alpha coronavirus 229E e NL63, beta coronavirus OC43 e HKU1, SARS-Cov , MERS ( Middle East respiratory syndrome) e COVID-19.  O coronavirus e caracterizado por uma disseminacao acelerada que possui como grupos de risco os idosos, pacientes imunocomprometidos e com doencas cronicas(hipertensos, portadores de cancer, diabeticos). Apesar de muitas pessoas estarem utilizando mascaras durante a pandemia, este EPI e indicado exclusivamente a individuos com casos suspeitos, a fim de evitar uma proliferacao.  A transmissao da infeccao ocorre por goticulas respiratorias ou pelo contato direto com secrecoes contaminadas, como saliva, espirro, aperto de mao, beijos, toques em objetos ou superficies que tenham sido expostas ao virus.  O periodo de incubacao e de 5 dias, com intervalos que podem chegar a 14 dias. Segundo os cientistas internacionais dos Centros de Controle e Prevencao de Doencas, o tempo de sobrevivencia do agente em superficies e: . *	Plastico: 72h . *	Aco inoxidavel: 72 . . *	Papelao: 24h . . *	Cobre: 4h . . *	Aerossolizada/poeiras: 3h . Legs todayyyy. As you'll see this session is more quad focused due to me hitting leg/pull in 3 days time.  1. Banded leg extension isometric hold- 45 seconds. 2 sets which will be progressed by increasing the time in the contracted position. This is programmed first to get the quad short whilst we can.  2. Db hammy curl. Programmed second for the same reason: as we fatigue a muscle, our ability to get it fully short diminishes. 2 sets. Top set in the 6-9 range with a decrease in load for the back off set aiming for higher reps.  3. BB back squat with controlled eccentrics - 2 sets. This acts as the main mechanical load for the session. I put my heals on a slightly raised platform to help with my poor ankle mobility, this is a simple alternative to squating on a ramp or wearing squat shoes.  4. Banded split squats - working the quad in its lengthened range. 1 top set(+10kg Db) and 1 back off (just banded). My front foot is elevated by 2 plates to increase range of motion.  5. Single Leg standing calve raise- 3 sets to failure. 2 second hold in both the contracted and lengthened position to prevent use of the Achilles' tendon stretch reflex.(Didn't film)  6. Db walking lunges drop set into bodyweight walking lunges- Aiming to pump as much blood into our legs as possible with these in order to create metabolic stress.Ps. Sabe aquele vegetal que fica sempre perto da batata-doce na feira, e tem a casca meio peluda e marrom? Esse ai e o inhame. Apesar de sua aparencia pouco atraente, o inhame e dos alimentos mais poderosos para fortalecer a imunidade e remover as impurezas do sangue.   Beneficios  Na medicina oriental, ele e recomendado por sua abundancia em zinco, mineral que ajuda a fortificar os ganglios linfaticos, linha de frente da defesa do nosso sistema imunologico. E fonte de fibras e carboidratos complexos (de baixo indice glicemico), responsaveis por equilibrar os niveis de acucar no sangue. Por ter vitaminas do complexo B e folato, e importante para a saude e a fertilidade do coracao. Tambem e rico em minerais como cobre, calcio, potassio, ferro, manganes, fosforo, e especialmente rico em potassio, que ajuda a controlar a frequencia cardiaca e a manter a pressao arterial.  "Tem que cozinhar antes?", "e igual a batata-doce?", "como comer o inhame?  E muito simples. Se preferir cozinhar, basta ferver uma panela com agua e adicionar o inhame, com casca e tudo. LET'S TALK ABOUT CORONAVIRUS  PREVENTION  In my opinion, there's still a lot of misinformation being spread. It's important not to panic. I'm not a doctor but there are things that people can do to stay safe and reduce the risk of infection. Honestly, the most helpful tips are basic:  1. Wash your hands with soap and water frequently, especially after going to the bathroom, before eating, and after blowing your nose, coughing, or sneezing;  2. Avoid touching your mouth, nose, or eyes;  3. Try to avoid people who are sick;  4. Cover your cough with a tissue or cough into your upper sleeve or elbow;  5. Carry and regularly use hand sanitiser.  You will find more useful tips on my blog, go check the link in bio. V Germanii bol'she ne razdeliaiut otkhody. A chto u nas?   RBK soobshchil, chto na vremia karantina v nekotorykh regionakh Frantsii, Italii i Germanii priostanovili razdel'nyi sbor otkhodov. V drugikh stranakh ogranichivaiut kolichestvo vyvozov, dezinfitsiruiut konteinery, prizyvaiut zhitelei skladyvat' otkhody v dvoinye meshki i vystavliat' ikh za dver'. Opasaiutsia, chto butylki, banki i bumaga nesut na sebe virus - v etikh stranakh ikh priravniali k meditsinskim otkhodami, kotorye nuzhno utilizirovat' osobym obrazom.   Seichas, deistvitel'no, vazhno priniat' mery i obezopasit' sotrudnikov, kontaktiruiushchikh s otkhodami. No i doma nuzhno sledovat' prostym pravilam, chtoby obezopasit' sebia i okruzhaiushchikh. Poetomu vmeste c pererabatyvaiushchim zavodom @ecotechnologies i moskovskimi operatorami po vyvozu otkhodov @ec_line_ru i @mkm.logistika my podgotovili dlia vas rekomendatsii, kak prodolzhat' razdeliat' otkhody na karantine i delat' eto be-zo-pas-no. Listaite kartochki    Eshche my khotim rasskazat', kakie mery bezopasnosti primeniaiut vyvoziashchie kompanii i pererabatyvaiushchie zavody.   K primeru, vse sotrudniki predpriiatii @ec_line_ru ezhednevno prokhodiat diagnostiku. Oni strogo sobliudaiut pravila profilaktiki, obespecheny spetsodezhdoi, perchatkami, respiratorami, dezinfitsiruiushchimi i moiushchimi sredstvami. Avtopark kompanii kazhdyi den' obrabatyvaiut antisepticheskim rastvorom. Musorovozy moiut ne tol'ko snaruzhi, no i vnutri. Konteinery i bunkery vo dvorakh takzhe obezzarazhivaiut soglasno grafiku, a otkhody vyvoziat, kak i vsegda - ezhednevno.   Na Tverskom zavode vtorichnykh polimerov @ecotechnologies tozhe deistvuiut usilennye mery bezopasnosti: bytovye pomeshcheniia, poly i ruchki agregatov obrabatyvaiut spetsial'nymi dezinfitsiruiushchimi sredstvami. Na predpriiatii razmeshcheny dozatory s antiseptikami. Kak i vsegda sortirovshchiki rabotaiut v prorezinennykh perchatkakh. Seichas obiazatel'no noshenie masok, khotia ran'she eto ostavalos' na usmotrenie sortirovshchika.

<<Kak ne svikhnut'sia na karantine?>> ili <<Laifkhaki dlia samoizolirovannykh>>        1. Obmani telo. Chtoby chuvstvovat' sebia luchshe, sdelai tak, chtoby telo ne chuvstvovalo izmenenii iz-za karantina. Priderzhivaisia svoego obychnogo rezhima, pitaniia, a takzhe takikh melochei kak grafik myt'ia volos i td.    2. Obmani mozgi. Ne, nu a chto. Poprobovat'   mozhno. Predstav' chto eto svoeobraznyi boikot. I sidet' doma bezvylazno - eto tvoio reshenie. Kak govoritsia, v liuboi neponiatnoi situatsii predstavliai sebia geroem fil'ma i zhdi kheppi enda.    3. Ispol'zui novye tekhnologii po maksimumu. Nalad' videosviaz' so svoei polovinkoi, druz'iami, esli takovye imeiutsia. Zarabotai v inete. Proidi onlain kursy povysheniia kvalifikatsii. Podtiani otsenki vo vremia distantsionnogo obucheniia.    4. Tebe eto seichas govoriat vse. I ia skazhu. Zaimis' uzhe nakonets tem, chto vsegda otkladyval. Voz'mi listochek, vypishi spisok vsekh tvoikh del, dlia kotoryi byla otmazka /net vremeni/, i poimi, chto karantina tebe ne khvatit vsio eto razgresti. Tak chto skuchat' nekogda.    5. Kak govoritsia. Dlia tekh, u kogo est' den'gi)) Skoree vsego, esli ty planiroval otdykh na mart/iiun', ty uzhe sdal bilety. Da i prosto esli planiroval kakuiu-to tusovku/podobnoe. Ne u vsekh, no u kogo-to iz-za vsei etoi figni i otmeny planov osvobodilis' otlozhennye den'gi. Konechno kazhdomu svoio. No moi sovet: potrat'. Seichas. Tipa, letom, esli vsia eta tema proidiot, tebe budut dostupny besplatnye razvlecheniia: te zhe progulki, obshchenie s liud'mi, radost' zhizni i td. A seichas mozhno i kupit' kakuiu-to nibud' figniu, kotoraia budet radovat' glaz i vozmozhno chem-to zanimat' na karantine.    #coronavirus #karantin #sididoma
