Recette de pain au Levain: Ingredients : - Farine d'orge complete - Farine de ble dur complete - Farine de ble tendre complete - levain ( a faire maison) - Gros sel ( une cuillere a soupe) - graines de votre choix ( ex: graines de lin, nigelle...) - une cuillere a soupe d'huile d'olive - eau tiede - son de ble ( pour le faconnage)  Ajouter tous les ingredients dans le bol du robot puis petrire pendant 5 a 10 min. Couvrire avec du film alimentaire et laisser lever la pate pendant 1 heure a 1h30 selon la temperature. Degazer la pate puis former des petites boules l'aide du son de ble. Laisser lever pendant 1h puis mettre au four programme special pain prechauffer a 220 degres. Surveiller la cuisson, laisser cuire pendant minimum 30min. Bonne degustation !  Pain delicieux et super bon pour la sante ! ... Hey les gars... Tout le monde dit qu'il "reve" de rester chez lui en pyjama a regarder la tele. Et quand l'Etat lui meme vous oblige a le faire, vous faites chier le monde a rester dehors ... ?   Faites vous l'integrale des Simpson, de GOT, Kaamelott, Friends, Walking Dead, Greys Anatomy, Mom, Californication, How I met Your Mother, Dr House, Malcom, Big Bang Theory et meme une Nounou d'Enfer !  Faites votre menage, votre jardinage, reprenez les cours de yoga que vous avez arrete au bout de 15jours en disant " j'ai pas le temps". Cet essai a la couture range depuis 6 mois ou encore ce cahier de coloriage "anti stress"  avec 3 pages entames. Sortez les 7 tomes de Harry Potter, l'integrale d'Agatha Christie, Victor Hugo, Tintin, le livre de 3e qui prend la poussiere depuis 20ans dans la bibliotheque pour rien, ...... Ou simplement reprenez les cours de vos gosses (ca vous fera pas de mal). Mais surtout :  RESTEZ CHEZ VOUS  Votre vie en depend.  La vie de vos proches en depend.  #stayhome #covid19

During these hard times of fear and self-isolation, it's incredibly fascinating to see how artists all around the globe reacted to this difficult and unexpected situation, creating art to connect people and make them feel less lonely and vulnerable.  @shrammusic and I, to connect with you even more, decided to launch an idea called "The self-isolation remixes". As you know the last Komponent's track is titled "Tell Me Something" - we thought it was the perfect one to choose from. Never like now, people want to connect, to talk, to communicate, using every possible means.  So what we ask you is to rework/remix our song "Tell Me Something" and to upload your version on your Soundcloud profile, [Komponent - Tell Me Something (Self-isolation remix by Your Name)], using the tag #theselfisolationremixes. Once ready we will create a Soundcloud playlist with all the works that you will send us.  Stems are intentionally made from recording sessions and not from mixing sessions, so you will have total control and freedom to cut, reinvent, compress and making some craziness on top of them.  Governments are actually taking different measures and decisions, sometimes not in a responsible way. We use this opportunity to tell you: "stay home and stay safe!". Use this time to be creative and to generate even more beauty.  1. Download stems - smarturl.it/selfisolationremixes  2. Rework/remix "Tell Me Something" 3. Upload on Soundcloud tagging #theselfisolationremixes  4. Send your link to perdurabo.official@gmail.com  We look forward to listening to your creativity. Until soon, share and stay safe!

O Projeto Florescer precisa da sua ajuda!  Acreditamos que a educacao seja a chave para a mudanca do mundo. O Projeto Florescer e uma concretizacao dessa crenca, pois oferece atividades pedagogicas, esportivas e ludicas a 20 criancas de Sobradinho II, DF.  Alem de voluntarios, temos 3 monitoras, contratadas para conseguirmos maior proximidade e qualidade nos servicos que sao oferecidos gratuitamente a comunidade, sem qualquer ajuda financeira do poder publico.  Todo o custeio do projeto e feito por doacoes, bazares e outras promocoes.  Porem, neste momento em que passamos pelo necessario isolamento social, interrompemos nossas atividades e enfrentamos dois grandes problemas:  1) A quarentena no DF impede que faxineiras, pedreiros, diaristas e tantos outros trabalhadores informais tenham renda para custear suas necessidades basicas. Nosso projeto, dentro de nossas limitacoes, procura amenizar o sofrimento dessas familias com a doacao de alimentos.  2) A quarentena tambem impede que realizemos bazares e eventos que nos ajudem a custear o projeto, especialmente o salario e encargos das tres dedicadas monitoras, as quais temos o dever de proteger nestes momentos de dificuldade.  Para contornar os dois problemas, estamos lancando uma campanha para conseguirmos pessoas que se compromentam com a doacao mensal de R$50,00 (se possivel, agende). Voce pode nos ajudar muito com a doacao mensal e tambem com o esforco de divulgacao da campanha a familiares e amigos, auxiliando enormemente o Projeto Florescer e a comunidade vulneravel de Sobradinho II neste momento de sofrimento coletivo. Estamos atentos as restricoes sanitarias e adotaremos os protocolos de higiene necessarios.  Adote esta causa. Divulgue essa ideia.  Saiba mais no link na bio. Vous ne pouvez changer ni ce qui arrive, ni les decisions qui ont ete prises.  Apprenez a prendre votre mal en patience. Arretez de vous plaindre. Et gardez en tete que : "Quand vous ne pouvez pas changer une situation, vous avez le pouvoir de changer votre facon de faire face a celle-ci". Cette periode de confinement va vous permettre de prendre du temps pour vous et surtout du temps de qualite.  Gardez vos bonnes habitudes, levez vous tot, faites du sport a la maison (des piliers de seances vont etre partagees prochainement) et continuez de mangez sainement.  Mettez ce temps a dispositon pour de bonnes choses.  Ne vous affalez pas dans votre canape devant Netflix ou du moins ne faites pas que ca de vos journees.  Concentrez vous sur tout ce qui apportera de la valeur ajoutee dans votre vie,  travaillez et accelerez sur vos projets personnels et professionnels. Toutes ces choses pour lesquelles vous n'avez pas de temps d'habitude.  Et surtout prenez du temps pour vous reposer et recharger vos batteries et pour prendre soin de vous et de votre entourage.  Bon courage a tous et gardez le sourire vous etes en vie et au final c'est la chose la plus importante.  #coronavirus #training #trainingtime #crossfit #crossfitter #crossfitgirl #crossfitrapace #fit #fitness #fitnessgirl #motivation #nevergiveup #quote #withlove

I'm on day 3 of isolation after a case was confirmed at work in my building wing. To be honest I think that many, if not most of us, have been exposed to the virus at this point and are in the incubation phase. -  The reason why quarantine and self isolation are so important right now, is because this virus takes up to 14 days to incubate. During this time infected people will not feel sick, but are still contagious. This makes it incredibly easy to unintentionally spread the virus. Additionally, while we need to be most concerned about our vulnerable populations, cases of young and otherwise healthy people getting seriously ill from this are beginning emerge as well. -  While I know many have been comparing death rates for other diseases as a method of deescalating worry, it's important to understand how quickly this is spreading. We do not have enough hospital facilities or respiratory equipment to serve the percentage of our population that will need care. The hope is that by slowing the spread of the virus it will allow more time for hospitals to adequately care for those are sick. -  When they made this video in Italy about 48 hours ago they were at 1,000 deaths. They are now at over 1,800, with 368 of those occurring within a 24 hour period. That was an over 25% day on day jump at the time. -  I urge you to please deeply consider your commonly accepted social behaviors right now and how they impact other people, especially the most vulnerable in our communities.

Day 7 of isolation!  -  I feel like I've turned a corner and being home has become very peaceful for me. -  I was very anxious my first few days transition into isolation, but that's completely gone away now. I'm honestly shocked at how quickly the days go by, including working from home. -  Incredibly grateful for everybody who has checked in on me this week and helped keep me company (virtually), for having my animals here with me, and for video conference calls. (It might sound silly, but being able to physically see each other makes a huge difference!) -  I would be remiss without saying that sadly, cases are popping up almost daily at work now. Stay safe everybody and take distancing measures very seriously!

Yeh duniya bhi kitni  Ajeeb hai nai? Yeh duniya,  Yeh log, yeh waqt.  Jisey dekho, harr kisi ke dilon me  Dard hai. Kuch zyada, kuch kam. Magar mayane toh sabki rkhti h na.  Yahan ek hi cheez ko do nazariye se bant'te hai log.  Jaise ki, Koi khushiyan manane ke liye peeta hai toh koi gham bhulane ke lie peeta hai.  Koi marne se darrta hai toh koi maut ke intezar me sirf zindagi kaat raha hai. Pareshan toh sbhi hai yahan, Magar suljhe hue sirf kuch. Muskuraate toh sbhi hai yahan, Magar khush sirf kuch. Zinda toh sabhi hai yahan, Magar jee rhe sirf kuch. Kuch beech raste me ummeedein chordete, kuch aur naye laga baith'te. Kuch chand palon ke laut aane ke aas me baithe rehte, Kuch aur naye banalete.  Khuda toh sirf ek hai,  Baant toh unhe bhi chand naamo ke saath diya in logon ne, Varna khudai ko tawajjah toh yahan sabhi log dete.  ~maherin _________________________________________  #poetry #hindipoetry #poetryisnotdead #indianpoem #desipoetry #urdupoetry #urdupoetrylovers #poetsofinstagram #poetsporn #poetspen #hindipoem #hindiurdumix #hindi #urdu #merealfaaz #dilkealfaaz #urdukealfaaz #poetry #writeups #indianpoetry #teenpoet #teenpoems #teenpoetry #stilllearning.#coronavirus #gocorona

Les tentations sont importantes, quand on passe les journees a la maison ! Il faut s'occuper avec des activites stimulantes. De nombreuses formes d'exercices existent en forme de videos sur YouTube. L'ennui et la frustration vont faire leur apparition. C'est tout a fait normal. Pour te preserver et ne pas laisser les emotions negatives t'envahir, maintiens-toi en forme. Instaure des regles et des objectifs chaque jour.  Si le confinement devient trop pesant et que tu te sens triste et isole, une equipe de psychologues sont joignables par visio-consultation. 10EUR de reduction avec le code de reduction FOR10, visio-consultation de 25 minutes ou 50 minutes. MILAN  Ahhh ... Notre tour du monde   Beaucoup nous pose la question a savoir : qu'en est il de notre tour du monde ? A ce jour, nous sommes tout comme vous, dans le meme bateau  Nous prenons connaissance quotidiennement de ce qu'il se passe en France et dans le reste du monde. Nous avons tendance a rester positives meme si honnetement, ca parait tres mal engage ! Alors oui tout est planifie, alors oui c'etait l'aventure & le projet d'une vie, alors oui nous allons y perdre... alors oui ce n'est que partie remise ! La vie est faite de surprises, de bonnes comme de mauvaises. Nous sommes toutes les 3 en bonne sante et c'est la : l'essentiel ! Nous sommes decues evidemment... Nous allons nous adapter en fonction de ce qu'il se passe, decaler en fonction d'une reprise a la << normale >> de la situation. Alors oui cela va etre un vrai casse tete, mais la encore : on ne va pas se plaindre... Nous avons la chance d'etre ensemble ce qui n'est pas le cas de tout le monde. Nous relativisons et nous pensons a tout le personnel soignants investi quotidiennement mais aussi a toutes les autres branches mobilisees pour continuer a faire vivre notre pays quelque soit le metier ! Bravo et merci  Soyons solidaires et bienveillants. Prenez soin de vous et restons chez nous ! . Cette photo prise l'ete dernier, lors de notre passage en Lombardie, en memoire a toutes ces personnes qui nous quittent chaque jour, toujours un peu plus, toujours un peu trop... . #milan #milano #restezchezvous #confinement #voyage #iorestoacasa #italie #italy #italia #duomomilano #travel #travelphotography #coronavirus #tourdumonde #solidarite #europe #earthpics #picoftheday #photooftheday #travelgram #travelblogger #traveladdict #voyager #tdm #lgbttravel #photo #lombardia #duomodimilano #forza #forzaitalia

WE ARE TOGETHER La lucha no es de hombres contra mujeres. Esta lucha no es por un puesto de superioridad entre un genero y otro.  La lucha es de los buenos ciudadanos, los buenos SERES HUMANOS contra los delincuentes y asesinos. La lucha es de ambos generos contra el machismo, misoginia , vulgaridad y violencia. Porque todos merecemos caminar tranquilos por la calle y estar tranquilos sobre donde esta nuestra familia y seres queridos.  Nuestra unica preocupacion deberia de estar en ser cada dia mejores personas, en superarnos, ayudar a los demas, ser mas fuertes y transmitir un mensaje positivo.  El machismo es ignorancia y el machismo empieza en casa. Es una enfermedad que se a transmitido de generacion en generacion incluso siendo algunas mujeres las portadoras. Asi que empecemos curando desde casa.  Siento pena por los hombres que nos ven a las mujeres como "inferiores" porque se estan perdiendo de su mejor complemento, su mejor equipo y de la gran energia y fortaleza que tenemos las mujeres para sentir tan abiertamente. -RC. #8M

La cuarentena se extiende y la verdad, no genero sorpresa. Sabemos que esto va a tomar tiempo y como dijo mi tio Socrates, solo sabemos que no sabemos nada... Somos seres tan domesticadxs por la rutina, que cuando se quiebra nuestro fragil sistema, nos llenamos de angustia y ansiedad.  Respira. Me parece genial que uses tu tiempo para aprender un curso nuevo, pero no recomiendo tapar tu angustia con cursos, sino hacerte cargo de tus emociones. Respira. Escucha a tu cuerpo, te duele algo? A que le temes? Puedes hacer algo al respecto? Si no puedes, vale la pena dedicarle tanta energia? Estas pensando mas en el futuro que en el presente? Respira. Siempre puedes compartir tus miedos con otrxs. Mira que si algo nos dice esta situacion, es que debemos comenzar a pensar en colectivo, como parte de un todo. Respira otra vez. #Repost do  @paulojubilut, professor do Biologia Total  QUANTO TEMPO O CORONAVIRUS DURA NA SUPERFICIE?                Galera, aqui segue um esquema mostrando quanto o coronavirus pode permanecer ativo em algumas superficies.              Esses numeros sao de um estudo feito com virus semelhantes ao novo coronavirus, que nao foi usado nessa analise. Isso quer dizer que esse tempo pode variar. O que temos ai e uma estimativa. E so pra vc ter uma ideia.              Lembrando que em locais acima de 30oC esse tempo mostrado na imagem e reduzido drasticamente, ja que esse virus e sensivel a temperaturas mais elevadas.              Mas Jubilut, como o coronavirus vai parar nesses lugares?              Quando uma pessoa tosse, espirra ou fala, ela elimina goticulas de saliva que se depositam nos mais diversos lugares. Se o virus estiver ativo num desses locais da imagem e vc colocar a mao em cima e depois levar a boca... ja era! Stressing out.  Losing our cool.  Buying every roll of toilet paper there is Isn't going to make it better.  Fear is not real.  It's a product  of the thoughts  we create.  The only place  that fear can exist is in our thoughts of the future.  It's a creation of our imagination  causing us to be afraid  of things  that do not at present  and may not EVER exist.  The thing is that  fear is the brains way of saying  there is something  important for you  to overcome.  Some of the greatest things  in life  are on the other side of fear.  Don't get me wrong.  Danger is real.  There are so many things.  Everyday.  That can make you sick.  Or even take your life.  But living in fear.  Fear of death. Fear of failure.  Fear of success.  Fear of love.  Fear of heartbreak.  Fear of a virus.  Living in fear is limiting.  It keeps us  from the best parts  of life.  It stops us from  truly fully living.  Stay calm my friends. A Federacao Brasileira de Bancos - Febraban - e seus bancos associados, sensiveis ao momento de preocupacao dos brasileiros com a doenca provocada pelo novo coronavirus, vem discutindo propostas para amenizar os efeitos negativos dessa pandemia no emprego e na renda. Entendem que se trata de um choque profundo, mas de natureza essencialmente transitoria.           Os bancos estao engajados em continuar colaborando com o Pais com medidas de estimulo a economia.           Nesse sentido, os cinco maiores bancos associados, Banco do Brasil, Bradesco, Caixa, Itau Unibanco e Santander estao abertos e comprometidos em atender pedidos de prorrogacao, por 60 dias, dos vencimentos de dividas de clientes pessoas fisicas, micro e pequenas empresas para os contratos vigentes em dia e limitados aos valores ja utilizados.           A excecao, a Caixa Economica Federal liberou o servico de pausa estendida para os clientes adimplentes ou com ate dois meses em atraso.           A Febraban informa ainda que os clientes nao precisam comprovar necessidade para suspender os pagamentos, precisam apenas informar que estao interessados nessa medida. A solicitacao para a suspensao dos pagamentos pode ser feita por Internet Banking, App e terminais de autoatendimento.           A exemplo de como solicitar o servico Pausa Estendida da Caixa Economica Federal, o mesmo pode ser acessado atraves do aplicativo Habitacao Caixa ou pelo Telesservico (telefones 3004-1105 para capitais e 0800-726-0505 para demais cidades), exclusivamente para contratos habitacionais Pessoa Fisica.           Para os contratos habitacionais com pessoas juridicas, o cliente devera entrar em contato com seu gerente para formalizar a solicitacao.           Confira abaixo o passo a passo para a solicitacao da pausa no pagamento das parcelas do financiamento:.           1. Acesse o aplicativo Habitacao Caixa.           2. Efetue o login.           3. Acesse a aba "Servicos".           4. Clique na opcao "Solicitar Pausa Emergencial".           5. Leia as orientacoes e clique em "Proximo".           6. Informe o numero do celular e autorize a Caixa a enviar SMS sobre a solicitacao.           7. Clique em "Solicitar Pausa".

No es facil hablar de 2 a 3 minutos de lo que Dios nos ha revelado, pero tu puedes descubrir mas cosas a traves de su palabra.  El nos dio vida.  Nueva Traduccion Viviente Efesios 2:1-5  1. Antes ustedes estaban muertos a causa de su desobediencia y sus muchos pecados. 2. Vivian en pecado, igual que el resto de la gente, obedeciendo al diablo el lider de los poderes del mundo invisible , quien es el espiritu que actua en el corazon de los que se niegan a obedecer a Dios. 3. Todos viviamos asi en el pasado, siguiendo los deseos de nuestras pasiones y la inclinacion de nuestra naturaleza pecaminosa. Por nuestra propia naturaleza, eramos objeto del enojo de Dios igual que todos los demas. 4. Pero Dios es tan rico en misericordia y nos amo tanto 5. que, a pesar de que estabamos muertos por causa de nuestros pecados, nos dio vida cuando levanto a Cristo de los muertos. (!Es solo por la gracia de Dios que ustedes han sido salvados!) Cuando aceptamos a Cristo debemos dar estos frutos:  Nueva Traduccion Viviente 2a Pedro 1:3-7  3. Mediante su divino poder, Dios nos ha dado todo lo que necesitamos para llevar una vida de rectitud. Todo esto lo recibimos al llegar a conocer a aquel que nos llamo por medio de su maravillosa gloria y excelencia. 4. Y, debido a su gloria y excelencia, nos ha dado grandes y preciosas promesas. Estas promesas hacen posible que ustedes participen de la naturaleza divina y escapen de la corrupcion del mundo, causada por los deseos humanos. 5. En vista de todo esto, esfuercense al maximo por responder a las promesas de Dios complementando su fe con una abundante provision de excelencia moral; la excelencia moral, con conocimiento; 6. el conocimiento, con control propio; el control propio, con perseverancia; la perseverancia, con sumision a Dios; 7. la sumision a Dios, con afecto fraternal, y el afecto fraternal, con amor por todos.  Busca a Cristo. El te ama. Dios te bendiga.  #venezuela #vzla #venezolano #caracas #cuarentena #coronavirus #covid19 #virus #Dios #cristo #Diostebendiga #pandemia #amor #corazon #biblia

Profissionais da saude, nao estao te fornecendo os Equipamentos de Protecao Individual (EPI)? Pois bem, notifique (POR ESCRITO) os Diretores clinicos e tecnicos, CRM/CFM, Ministerio Publico, Secretario da Saude e a Comissao de Etica da instituicao. Se nao ha condicoes de trabalho, nao ha que se falar em omissao de socorro, caso o trabalho do medico/enfermeiro seja suspenso (algo que nao queremos, por isso exija posicao/providencia de seus gestores). Fundamentacao do que foi dito: art. 7, XXII, da Constituicao Federal; NR-32; Lei 13.979/20; e Codigo de Etica Medica, Item IV. Refriso, e devido a estes profissionais o pagamento de adicional de insalubridade. Ha link para denuncia no site da AMB. Em caso de duvidas, procure um advogado. #direitomedico #direitodasaude #direitodotrabalho #coronavirus #quarentena #linhadefrente #profissionaisdasaude  ___________________  Fonte @samanthatakahashi_

#coronavirus - PLANOS DE SAUDE TERAO R$10 BILHOES DA UNIAO  O ministro da Saude, Luiz Henrique Mandetta, afirmou que o governo vai facilitar a liberacao de R$ 10 bilhoes aos planos de saude. O valor faz parte de um fundo garantidor, vinculado a Agencia Nacional de Saude Suplementar (ANS), composto por recursos das operadoras.  Com a medida, o governo quer garantir que os planos de saude consigam usar 20% do fundo garantidor, cujo valor total e de R$ 53 bilhoes. A expectativa, de acordo com o ministro, e que as operadoras usem os recursos para comprar equipamentos e reforcar leitos. O objetivo e nao sobrecarregar ainda mais o sistema publico de saude em meio ao avanco do novo coronavirus nos proximos meses. Repost: @cafecomsociologia  Fonte: @epocanegocios

All of our lives have changed dramatically over the last few days as the COVID 19 pandemic has evolved. We are facing an issue of enormous scale that is affecting every part of our world. Being a healthcare provider working on the frontlines in a pulmonary medical ICU during a time when others are going into isolation has been incredibly challenging. There's a lot of uncertainty ahead, but we as humans need to work together and show each other kindness in order to survive.  To my fellow healthcare providers who are also making sacrifices and working tirelessly to ensure patients receive the care they need, I appreciate you and I'm with you. To those who have the ability to engage in social distancing/ avoid non-essential interactions thank you for dealing with the frustrations/inconveniences/social & financial implications of this and for doing your part to help reduce spread of this disease. Hope that you are able to use this time to engage in self care.  We all have the ability to make a greater impact on humankind and help each other get through this. Da, ruki myt' obiazatel'no nado kogda prishel s ulitsy. No POSTOIaNNO myt' zhto uzh slishkom. (govorit ta, kotoraia posle kazhdogo prikosnoveniia veshchi, moet ruki) . . Esli vy dumaete chto vas spaset obychnaia tkanevaia maska, to vy ne pravy. Eto ved' obychnaia tkan' na vashem litse. Mikroby vseravno proidut! K tomu zhe litso dolzhno dyshat'. Esli vy kashleite, eto ne znachit chto vy bol'ny korona virusom!!!!! . . Est' 3 tipa liudei:  1) -- AAAAA, KORONA VIRUS!!! MY VSE UMREM! OBIaZATEL'NO ODEVAITE MASKI PERED TEM KAK VYKhODIT' NA ULITsU!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! 2) -- Ia v nego voobshche ne veriu. Mne vseravno.... 3) Liudi, ne volnuites'! Vse khorosho! Ne panikuite! Bol'she paniki, men'she spaseniia! Ot grippa bol'she liudei umiraet! ........ Ia 3 tip. A kakoi tip ty? Chto ty dumaesh' ot etom? PURE - Strength + Wellness At Home Workout #9 Please see corresponding up-loaded video for Workout #9  Legs and Core   Each round should take between 15-20 minutes, so depending on the time, and energy you have, 2 or 3 rounds, bang in another if you feel like it!!   1) Jumprope or Boxers Shuffle - 30sec.  2) Legs-Front Squats - 24/20/16 (Push through the heels). 3) Core- Heeldigs 12/10/8(Keep the Lower-Back pressured against the floor). 4) Jumprope or Boxers Shuffle - 30sec.  5) Lunge Pulses 12/10/8 each side (Breathe in on the lowering exhale on the lifting). 6) Baby Rolls - 12/10/8 (Slow deliberate movement). 7) Jumprope or Boxers Shuffle - 30sec.  Double or Single Hip Bridge Extensions - 24/20/16 doubles or 12/10/8 singles (Squeeze the Hamstrings and Glutei at the top). 9) V-Sit Rotations 24/20/16 (Rotate through the Shoulders). 10) Jumprope or Boxers shuffle - 30sec.  11) Lateral Step Lunges - 12/10/8 each side. (Sit Back into the Hips weight on the Heels). 12) Plank Variation - 60sec (Take a rest when needed but complete a total of 60sec). Minimal rest between exercises, get a bit of your breath back, but keep up the intensity at a good pace for yourself to attain physical stress for adaptation.  Complete the exercises at a pain free range of motion, speed and weight that is applicable to yourself, this is your call. The greater the applied safe stress on the body, the greater the adaptation in fitness and strength. Don't forget your quality nutrition and quality recovery/rest to aid in that adaptation from the stimulus.  Hope this finds everyone staying Strong and Well. El uso de barbijo es util unicamente para:  Las personas con COVID-19 no propaguen la enfermedad.  Debes usarlo si se te presentan los sintomas respiratorios caracteristicos de la COVID-19 (fiebre, dolor de garganta, resfrio, tos).  Tambien debe usarlo el personal de salud que asiste a personas con enfermedad respiratoria.  Pacientes con infeccion respiratoria con la deambulacion por el hospital. . [?][?]COMO PONERSE, USAR, QUITARSE Y DESECHAR EL BARBIJO?[?][?] .  Antes de ponerse un barbijo, lavese las manos con un desinfectante a base de alcohol o con agua y jabon. .  Cubrase la boca y la nariz con el barbijo y asegurese de que no haya espacios entre su cara y la mascara.  Evite tocar el barbijo mientras la usa; si lo hace, lavese las manos con un desinfectante a base de alcohol o con agua y jabon. Cambiese de barbijo tan pronto como este humeda y no reutilice los barbijos de un solo uso. .  Para quitarse el barbijo: quitesela por detras (no toque la parte delantera de la barbijo); desechela inmediatamente en un recipiente cerrado; y lavese las manos con un desinfectante a base de alcohol o con agua y jabon. . #cuarentena #quedateencasa #prevencion #farmacia #farmaceutica #cordoba #argentina #coronavirus #cov19

[?] Como senala la jirafa, el problema esta en la IDEALIZACION. * !?[?] ?Que es la idealizacion? La idealizacion es ver en el otro solo cosas positivas, y a veces, aun sin que existan. Idealizar es ver parcialmente, dejando de lado las partes menos atractivas de una persona. Esto suele suceder al principio de las relaciones y coincide con la etapa de enamoramiento. * [?]?Cuanto tiempo puede durar este estado? Eso va a depender de cada persona, pero no es casual que en la actualidad las parejas no suelan durar mas de dos anos en promedio, que es el periodo en el que la idealizacion se sostiene. En una epoca que empuja hacia ideales imposibles, las personas parecen tener miedo de relacionarse en profundidad con alguien, y se asustan frente a la intimidad real. Cuando llega el momento de enfrentarse con la otra persona tal cual es, llega la separacion, y nuevamente van en busca de un nuevo ideal que estara destinado al mismo fin si es que no modifican los patrones. * [?] ?Como se puede cambiar este circulo vicioso? Conociendonos a nosotros mismos en primer lugar, y aceptando en nosotros los defectos y virtudes, para recien asi poder verlos el el otro. Prometiendo menos imposibles del tipo de "juntos para siempre", porque no sabemos como nos vamos a sentir manana, y no esta bien perpetuar relaciones en nombre de ideales imposibles. * [?] El amor existe. Las relaciones duraderas y lindas son posibles, pero solo si somos personas responsables y no negamos nuestra humanidad y la del otro, vamos a poder acceder a ellas. Si todas tus relaciones tienen el mismo fin, y no sabes como salirte del circulo vicioso, tal vez sea momento de empezar terapia. * * *  Consultorio en Microcentro.  Atencion online. . How productive can you work from home?  It is an interesting experience for those who have never done home office before.  How do you make sure to be as productive as at work?  It has certainly needed some adjustments when I first worked from home.  Find belowmy learnings.  This is how to boost productivity at your home office: .  Find a quiet corner  There are so many potential distractions. Therefore, find the most boring corner in the house or apartment and turn it into a working area. .  Turn off notifications  Our mobiles represent a major distraction these days. Devote time in the late afternoon or evening to go through your emails or social media messages. Guess what, most messages can wait. And if you need a channel of communication (e.g. to be there for your spouse or kids), choose one platform, turn these notifications on and share it only with the people you must communicate with on short notice. The rest can wait! . [?][?] Deep working & conscious breaks  Many duties (e.g. laundry, cooking, cleaning, etc) can prevent us from working. Allow yourself short breaks, but use the time in between wisely. Deep working means nothing else than being fully focused on your tasks. Be responsible when it comes to the frequency and lengths of your breaks. Ask yourself, would you take such a break at work?

. It is not even three months ago when we wished us a happy new year. Nobody expected the year 2020 start the way it did.  Many organizations are hit hard at the moment.  The Corona pandemic came as unexpected as it brutally hit our private and professional lives.  Company leaders are confronted with the difficult task of navigating their organization through these heavy storms.  This is how to lead your organization in these uncertain times: .  Perspective  Make yourself aware that the curve will flatten. There will be a time after Corona and if we all act responsibly this time will rather come sooner than later. Companies start adjusting by sending their workforce to home office. .  Prepare for the time after  Once you realize that there is light at the end of the tunnel and you have done all you can for the organization to survive this pandemic, you can start preparing for the time after. How can you use the crisis to align your values with your message (branding), optimize your product/service and bind your people to the organization? .  Take care of your people  Your employees will carry you through these uncertain times and they will also help you come back stronger after the crisis. Is it too much asked to be a leader in this crisis who puts his/her people first? One simple way would be weekly surveys. How do they feel? Has the organization provided all needed for them to work at home as efficiently and productive as at the workplace? Does the communication within the team work? Do employees get the same support by their direct manager as before? Does the company provide enough information for the employee to feel safe? Are there processes in place for different teams to communicate with each other? And so on... . Artist credit: Nicholas Sampson

Como tornar os fins de semana diferentes dos dias de semana se, aos 24 dias de quarentena, os dias parecem todos iguais?! Continuamos a ter alguma dificuldade em organizarmo-nos, e se ha dias que correm bem, ha outros que correm muito muito mal. Aos sabados temos comecado o dia com panquecas e cafe e um pequeno almoco tardio com calma, sem corrermos para nos irmos sentar ao computador a trabalhar. O almoco desliza para tarde porque entretanto fazem-se as limpezas. De tarde e tempo de por as conversas em dia com amigos e familia. Na semana passada fizemos pizza via skype com Cascais (receita mais logo nos stories). Hoje o programa da noite e vermos um concerto da @lfilmorchestra juntos com amigos italianos e portugueses (que entretanto andei a fazer publicidade em todos os grupos whatsapp). Amanha sera mais um domingo lento em que se prepara a semana (continuamos a tentar...). E por ai como se organizam? Cuando hablamos de DERECHO SUCESORIO, nos referimos a la transmision de derechos y obligaciones de la persona fallecida a sus herederos.    Ahora bien, existen dos tipos de sucesiones:    1)  TESTAMENTARIA: Donde la persona, previo a su fallecimiento, redacta un documento (testamento) donde deja asentado la reparticion de sus bienes.    2)  AB INTESTATO: Se aplica cuando la persona fallecida no elaboro ningun testamento previo, por lo que se aplican las disposiciones del Codigo Civil y Comercial de la Nacion para la reparticion de sus bienes.     ?DONDE SE INICIA LA SUCESION?      Se inicia ante los Tribunales del ultimo domicilio del causante.      ?QUIEN/QUIENES PUEDEN INICIARLA?   1)  El conyuge, los herederos y legatarios      2)  El albacea (ejecutor testamentario)      3)  Los acreedores de quienes heredan      4)  El Consejo Nacional de Educacion (en caso de herencias vacantes)     5)  Todos los que tengan en la sucesion algun derecho declarado por las leyes.      ?UN SOLO HEREDERO PUEDE INICIAR LA SUCESION?      Si, la sucesion puede ser iniciada por uno solo de los herederos, pero es necesario que notifique a los demas de la apertura del sucesorio.      ?QUE DOCUMENTACION SE NECESITA PARA INICIAR UNA SUCESION?      Se requiere:      1)  Partida de defuncion del titular de los bienes a transmitir.      2)  Todas las partidas  que acrediten el vinculo con el causante (partida/s de nacimiento y/o libreta de matrimonio)      3)  Titulos de propiedad de los bienes a transmitir.     [?] [?] Es importante saber que en caso no contar con alguna documentacion, puede solicitarse una nueva  ante los organismos publicos. RECARGA TU SISTEMA INMUNOLOGICO  Nuestra formula exclusiva es una infusion intravenosa para estimular su sistema inmune y ayudar a prevenir enfermedades relacionadas con los virus y microbios comunes.  Recordar que la Vitamina C solo puede ser entregada en Megadosis mediante via intravenosa. Por via oral la absorcion no es optima y su dosis seria Antiinflamatoria. Para combatir infecciones necesitamos dosis PROOXIDANTES, las cuales solo son logradas mediante sueroterapia.  Nuestra terapia esta formulada para maximizar la respuesta inmune mediante nutrientes fundamentales en la desintoxicacion del cuerpo y en el sistema de defensa natural.  Recibir estos nutrientes a traves de la terapia intravenosa mejora su absorcion, entregandolos directamente al torrente sanguineo. Empatia: o respeito e a coragem de se colocar no lugar do outro.  De enxerga-lo e tentar ajuda-lo, uma palavra que temos usado tanto ultimamente.   Ela e o laco de fato invisivel que tenta nos aproximar mesmo estando distantes uns dos outros.   Ela nos faz repensar nossos lugares de privilegios diante do que vem acontecendo.  Ela traz a forca que as vezes, em mais um dia de confinamento, nos falta!   Ela esta bem do nosso lado, na tv, no vizinho, na calcada do seu condominio...  E que normalmente nao percebemos!   Que tenhamos a empatia cada vez mais do nosso lado, que nos apoiemos!   Eu estou com ela, e por estar com ela, eu estou com voce!          #fisioterapia #daniellemelhadofisioterapia #fisio #bemestar #empatia #ficaemcasa #amor #quarentena #covid #covid19 #quarentena #coronavirus

Reading For The Collective (#coronavirus)  WORRY (Reversed) 5 of Disks [Pentacles] Numerology of The number 5: Fives are about changes and disruptions, and Pentacles are about the physical. The energy of this card is one of sudden setbacks - business, financial, or even health. *Keep in mind that this card can also pertain to the FEAR OF such things. It is possible that what this card shows is a magnification of our emotions and focus around current events. This is not to discount what is going on, but to check in and make sure we aren't letting the various what-ifs rule us. Remember, even amid these big problems, we do have power. It's also possible that things are not as bad as they seem but clouded by negative thoughts. We must keep in mind that although we may not have control of the difficulties we face, the power lies in our reactions. If you are worrying yourself over things you cannot control, you are only weakening your immune system. Instead, put yourself, your healing, and spiritual desire front and center. No one is more important to you than you. ----> THE SUN XIX * We are walking from the 5 of Pentacles energy towards the Sun. We all need to stop worrying or thinking of the endless list of negative possibilities to this situation. Don't let fear control you, be mindful of your thoughts and stay positive, things will get better.  In this time of uncertainty and possibly isolation, also remember that just as one could isolate themselves indoors we can also be self contained OUTDOORS, in the light of the sun. The sun (literally speaking and also symbolically) will be playing a very important role in a form of PROGRESS or type of healing element - to many of the problems we as a collective are facing at this time. (whether these problems are  physical/Mental or spiritual) This can mean a number different things from being out in the sun, being out in nature, feeling the rays of the sun - changing the mindsets of the collective. SO proud to be part of this team. We folks at @ibm @weatherchannel just launched our latest product that provides timely evidence-based, location-based specific information about Covid-19 cases in our community. As of now, we are only providing evidence within the US, but in the upcoming weeks, are going global. What differentiates this product is that it shows you the trend line on an ongoing basis, down to the county level!  Please visit  or download The Weather Channel App for iOS or Android to view the product.  This is one of the most challenging projects I've ever worked on in my career, both from a professional and emotional standpoint.  It has always been my mission as a designer to "design" the change I want to see in the world, and this is my first step for an app with 45 million users! The data on this sensitive subject matter is very complex out there, some of it is conflicting. So we wanted to help by providing a trusted source to everyone; the CDC which is hyperlocal. (1/2) "How would you describe your fighting style?" "I'm a counter fighter. I monopolise on people's habits. For me its not about getting in the ring and beating someone up. It's about outsmarting someone. It's a chess match, who can think as many moves ahead. I try to throw the strikes that people aren't used to, the unfamiliarity makes them hesitate and then I make them pay for it. Critical thinking is everything. I don't deal well with pressure but I'm good at nullifying it. If you can concentrate under high pressure, you can do it anywhere. I don't like aggression. Anyone can do aggression, anyone can stand in front of you and punch you till you drop. My hardest fights have been where my opponent has out-smarted me and nullified my best weapon" "Was there a significant moment that helped shape your style?" "Yes. Actually there is one. It was a cross over point fighting tournament, taekwondo vs kickboxing. I had a taekwondo background and was about 15/16 years old. I was up against a 20-year-old kickboxer and at the time he seemed like a fully-grown man to me. The people he had fought before me on that night were all left with busted lips, heavy nose bleeds. So admittedly I was very nervous and as a little kid I sat there thinking this man is going to kill me.  During our fight, he kept steam rolling me and pushing me on the backfoot. He was too much for me to deal with. With point fighting there is no ring, it's a square mat with a judge seated on each corner. My opponent kept applying pressure, knocking me off the matts twice. The third time he did that I fell over one of the corner judges. She was a woman, I knocked her over and thought shit this is really embarrassing, this guy is really embarrassing me. He knew this was affecting me, so he charged towards me once again, but I timed him and managed to hit him with a jumping back kick. He couldn't fight me from that point on. That one moment, that one counter move, made me realise I have good timing and reaction speed. The jumping back kick became my trademark move, I still use it nearly every fight"  #quarantinestories #boxing #mma #anthonyjoshua  #kickboxing #muaythai #k1 #covid19 #shareblackstories

My chast' tselogo   Nu chto zh, seichas nastupilo vremia toi samoi ChISTKI. Ia dumaiu, osoznanie suti i puti reshenii pomozhet nam izbezhat' mnozhestva trudnostei.  Priroda ustala ot griazi, musora, zla, vreda, stradanii i neschastii, nanesennykh ei chelovekom. Chelovek - chast' prirody. My vse, pomimo khoroshego, privnosim takzhe MUSOR, kak i v svoiu zhizn', tak i v zhizn' drug druga. Davaite delit'sia svetom, dobrom, zabotoi, privnosit' liubov', zdorov'e, garmoniiu.  Seichas budet nelegko absoliutno vsem. A raz uzh my dokatilis' do etogo, khotia skoro i fakticheski mozhem fatal'no okazat'sia v vynuzhdennoi sotsial'noi izoliatsii, luchshim nashim resheniem bylo by - derzhat'sia druzhno VMESTE.  V odinokoi, samostoiatel'noi greble v sobstvennoi lodke, ne zabyvaite o tom, chto my plyvem v odnom bol'shom OKEANE zhizni. Vse vmeste.  Eto nashe i instinktivnoe, prirodnoe i sotsial'noe - byt' 'v' i 's' obshchestvom.  Ne khochetsia zabyvat' ni  o  s e b e , ni  d r u g  o  d r u g e.  Razumnee prinimat' vsiu slozhivshuiusia situatsiiu so smireniem, ne lezt' v ochag, ne provotsirovat' i proveriat' sud'bu i svoe zdorov'e, ne podnimat' kipish', no i ne otchaivat'sia, vpadat' v tosku, bezumnoe otchaian'e, depressii ili tem bolee bezumstvovat', priatat'sia, bezhat' ot vsego i vsekh vokrug.  Poetomu s trepetom i zabotoi otnosites' k sebe, sobstvennoi gigiene, k vzaimootnosheniiam s blizkimi i okruzhaiushchimi. Okh i kak by nepriiatno i bol'no ne zvuchalo, no v kontse kontsov nadlezhashchim obrazom davaite otnositsia k chistote i poriadku v svoei zhizni, inache priroda ochistit sebia v tom chisle i za schiot NAS, nezdorovykh, lishnikh, slabykh, nenuzhnykh, bespoleznykh vreditelei.  Bud'te vsegda proinformirovany i sobliudaite mery predostorozhnosti!  No ne zanimaites' tupost'iu, pozhaluista! Ona ne koronovirus, i mne inogda kazhetsia, chto imenno GLUPOST' - samoe opasnoe ZLEIShEE ZLO iz vsekh. Tupost', kazhetsia, ne imeet protivoiadiia i kakikh-libo protivodeistvii, ne karaetsia i slovno ne poddaetsia nikakim chelovecheskim ob'iasneniiam, zakonam.  Tupost' - eto edinstvennoe, chto peredaetsia cherez instagram i drugie sotsial'nye seti!Bud'te na cheku! Ona opasnee liubogo virusa, i navredit tak, chto vy togo i ne zametite.   Beregite sebia i blizkikh! Da budem zhe my po otdel'nosti, no vmeste! [?]   [?]

" Liudstvo otrimalo same tu khvorobu, iaka bula potribna iomu.  Mi perestali tsinuvati zdorov'ia, i tomu otrimali tsiu khvorobu, shchob usvidomiti, shcho pro zdorov'ia potribno dbati.  Mi perestali tsinuvati prirodu, i tomu otrimali taku khvorobu, shchob nashe perebuvannia v prirodi bulo minimal'nim.  Mi perestali vmiti spivisnuvati v sim'iakh, i tomu tsia khvoroba zakrila nas v nashikh budinkakh, shchob mi znovu navchilisia zhiti iak sim'ia.  Mi perestali povazhati liudei pokhilogo viku tomu otrimali tsiu khvorobu, shchob zgadati, iaki voni vrazlivi.  Mi perestali tsinuvati medichnikh pratsivnikiv i farmatsevtiv, shchob diznatisia, iaki voni nezminni.  Mi perestali povazhati vchiteliv, i tomu nam tsia khvoroba zakrila shkoli, shchob bat'ki sami mogli sprobuvati vchiti.  Mi dumali shcho mozhemo kupiti vse, buti vsiudi i z kozhnim z kim khochemo zustritisia, tomu mi otrimali tsiu khvorobu, shchob usvidomiti, shcho tse ne ie zvichainistiu.  Nami zavolodila Mamona*, vil'nii chas mi provodili v supermarketakh, tomu nam tsia khvoroba yikh zakrila, shchob zrozumiti, shcho shchastia mi ne mozhemo pridbati.  Bagato uvagi mi pridiliali nashomu zovnishn'omu vigliadu i  zavzhdi porivniuvali sebe z inshimi, tomu nam tsia khvoroba zakrila oblichchia maskami, shchob zrozumiti, shcho nashoyi krasi tam nemaie.  Dumali, shcho mi gospodari na tsii zemli, i tomu otrimali tsiu khvorobu, shchob nas shchos' duzhe miniatiurne i nevidime moglo priruchiti, dati nam putivnik i trokhi smirennia.  Tsia khvoroba v nas bagato zabiraie, ale v toi zhe chas daie mozhlivist' bagato chogo navchitisia i zrozumiti te, shcho v zhitti naivazhlivishe. Mi otrimali khvorobu zshitu po nashim mirkam. Mozhlivo, iak liudstvu, vona naspravdi bula nam potribna. Corona is on the loose and everyone seems to loose their minds. I don't know what the situation is in your countries - but next to me Tom, Dick and Harry start panic buyings. This is why I want to share my two cents on a - supposed - difference between "Prepping" and "Preparedness". When I think of "Prepping", I see in my mind's eye, guys patting their M16 in a bunker full of canned food. (Okay, cliche) But my point is this: "Prepping" as I understand it, is putting a massive amount of energy and resources in preparing for the ultimate-MCA - no matter how improbable. "Preparedness" on the other hand is about considering a broad variety of possible scenarios, to have a plan (or two) and to be forearmed for the most probable of them.  So the key difference (if there is any, as in my opinion) between "Prepping" and "Preparedness" would be probability and efficiency. Let's get back to the Corona Virus: from all that we currently know it's probably slightly more dangerous than the common flu. At least, it's not Captain Trips! So if people, who have never dealt with emergency preparations in their lives, now start to build up stocks as if civilization is going to collapse tomorrow, I just can find that ridiculous. There will be, however, some serious economic consequences in the long run, but that's quite another cup of tea.  What do you think about the whole topic? "El mundo nos rompe a todos, y luego algunos se hacen mas fuertes en las partes rotas." Ernest Hemingway.                   [?]El arte tradicional japones de reparar la ceramica rota con un adhesivo fuerte rociado despues con polvo de oro, se llama Kintsugi.                    Ellos creen que cuando algo ha sufrido un dano y tiene una historia, se vuelve mas hermoso.                    El resultado es que la ceramica no solo queda reparada sino que es aun mas fuerte que la original.                    Llevemos esta imagen al terreno de lo humano, al mundo del contacto con los seres que queremos y que, a veces, danamos o nos lastiman.                    !Que importante entender que los vinculos lastimados pueden repararse con los hilos dorados del amor y volverse mas fuertes!                    La idea es que cuando algo valioso se dana, una estrategia a seguir es no ocultar su fragilidad ni su imperfeccion; sino repararlo con algo que haga la funcion del oro (fortaleza, virtudes,...).                    La "senal" de la imperfeccion y la fragilidad, pero tambien de la resiliencia (la capacidad de recuperarse) son dignas de ser mostradas.                    La resiliencia distingue dos componentes: la resistencia frente a la destruccion, es decir, la capacidad de proteger la propia integridad, bajo presion y, por otra parte, mas alla de la resistencia, la capacidad de forjar un comportamiento vital positivo pese a las circunstancias dificiles.  Todas las personas tenemos la capacidad de sobreponernos a un estimulo adverso, pero el uso decidido y firme de esta capacidad es lo que nos hace realmente resilientes.  Afrontar la adversidad con humor es propio de personas resilientes. Ser capaces de reirnos de la adversidad y sacar una broma de las situaciones dificiles nos ayuda a superarlas y mantenernos fuertes y optimistas ante la incertidumbre. Esto no quiere decir que en mitad de la que esta cayendo con el #covid tengamos que usar el humor de forma obligadas, sino buscar ratos felices.  La creencia de que uno puede aprender con sus experiencias, sean estas positivas o negativas nos permite seguir creciendo y madurando a lo largo de la vida.  #coronavirus

"Sera que devo contratar um especialista em Marketing para o meu projeto?"., "Vale a pena?". "Eu mesmo nao poderia dar conta disso?" O trabalho de elaborar e executar estrategias de marketing digital nao e algo tao simples. Delegar essa funcao a um especialista permite que voce foque em suas funcoes, e e uma forma de garantir que as estrategias nao sejam feitas as pressas ou de forma desatenta.  Ja pensou no prejuizo que voce pode ter ao investir um valor alto em uma publicidade que nao foi bem planejada ou executada?  Especialistas de marketing possuem um conhecimento especifico que dificilmente voce teria, mesmo com muito estudo: o conhecimento pratico.  Quantas vezes voce teve que consertar um erro que impediu a publicacao de um anuncio no Facebook, por exemplo?  O marketing e uma atividade que apresenta ramificacoes. O mesmo acontece com o marketing digital. Alguns profissionais sao especialistas em redes sociais, outros em e-mail marketing, entre outras areas.  Trabalhar com especialistas e a melhor forma de garantir que a sua equipe vai ter o suporte necessario para executar com perfeicao diferentes estrategias ou etapas de uma mesma estrategia. . El arte de la guerra es un libro escrito por el general y estratega militar Sun Tzu hace aproximadamente 2.500 anos en la antigua China.  Es un tratado sobre practica militar y estrategia de guerra que se fundamenta en principios de la doctrina taoista.  El arte de la guerra, en este sentido, es un texto que nos ayuda a comprender mejor la naturaleza de los conflictos y a analizar y evaluar las mejores alternativas para su solucion.  Algunas de las ensenanzas fundamentales del libro son que lo ideal es vencer sin luchar y que la guerra se basa en el engano y la confusion del enemigo. Asimismo, se destaca la importancia de saber ajustarse a las condiciones, ser capaces de defender las ventajas, aprovechar las oportunidades y tener claridad de vision y un solido liderazgo.  Es considerado uno de los mejores y mas vigentes libros de estrategia militar de todos los tiempos. Sus advertencias han tenido influencia a lo largo de la historia sobre grandes estrategas de la guerra y la politica de Oriente y Occidente, como Nicolas Maquiavelo, Napoleon Bonaparte o Mao Zedong[?] . . . . . . #dios #amor #covid19 #coronavirus #motivacion #autoayuda #mejorar #instagram #ebook #bookdigital #digital #elcambio #theshift #psicologia  #elartedelaguerra #arte#guerra#empresas#negocios #SunTzu #Tzu

Zhenshchine priiatno, kogda ee baluiut, no rastsvetaet ona lish' togda, kogda muzhchina khochet ee udivit'. Kogda ne prikhoditsia govorit' o svoikh zhelaniiakh kvartalami, kogda ty ne zamechaesh', chto upominula o svoei mechte, a on zapomnil i realizoval. Mne kazhetsia, tak postupaiut tol'ko te muzhchiny, kotorye istinno liubiat. Mogut zhe liubit' iskrenne i napolnuiu tol'ko te, kto zhivet bez kompleksov i strakhov, kto vediot sebia otkryto, ne boitsia poluchat' i otdavat' teplo. Nemnogo filosofii pod puer i ty v kotoryi raz ponimaesh', chto liudi stradaiut ot togo, chto boiatsia liubit'. I, kak mne kazhetsia, boiazn' est' semechki, chtoby ne bylo appenditsita, menee strannaia, chem boiazn' chuvstv.

Kto menia ochen' khorosho znaet, tot znaet moiu liubov', a tochnee uvazhenie k iumoru, no seichas ne ob etom. Byl u menia period v zhizni, kogda ia izuchala istoriiu sitkomov, pridumyvala idei i prikrepliala doma na doske, to loglainy, to idei epizodov, to konflikty, to novykh personazhei... Dlia chego? Prosto tak, potomu chto nravilos' i vdokhnovlialo. Eto krutoi zhanr, kotoryi perezagruzhaet ochen' bystro ot real'nosti. On uchit prostoi istine. Vse peredriagi reshatsia i k kontsu epizoda, vse verniotsia na iskhodnye pozitsii. Glavnoe pravilo sitkoma i est' zhiznennoi pravdoi.  V proshlom i v etom godu u menia byli epizody v neskol'kikh sitkomakh. I poka oni gotoviatsia k vykhodu v efir, ia mechtaiu o vertikal'noi roli v takom formate.  Ponimanie, chto kto-to budet smotret', ulybat'sia i nakhodit' novye sily - motiviruet luchshe liubogo Toni Robbinsa.

S devochek nado sduvat' pylinki  Seichas budut protestovat' mnogie: feministki, zhenshchiny, kotorym prochistili mozgi ikh muzhchiny, a tak zhe  muzhchiny i zhenshchiny s kompleksami i psikhotravmami.  Ves' etot informatsionnyi musor o ravenstve polov smeshon. Posmotrite na svoi myshtsy. Oni takie zhe sil'nye, kak u muzhchiny? Ponabliudaite za emotsional'nym sostoianiem. Ono takoe zhe stabil'noe, kak u muzhchin? Da net zhe. Gormony-peregormony i eto neplokho. My za odin den' meniaem sotni sostoianii, chtoby muzhchiny ne nachali v etoi zhizni zasypat' ot rutiny. Mne kazhetsia, tak pridumal sozdatel' i on tochno khorosho produmal bibliiu personazhei i dlia interesnykh siuzhetov sdelal nas maksimal'no raznymi.  Da. Zhenshchina chasto bolee spokoinaia, inogda fizicheski sil'nee, no eto ne znachit, chto ei ne prikhoditsia v razy bol'she prikladyvat' usilii i otdavat' vsiu sebia raznym protsessam zhizni.  Mne kazhetsia, chtoby u devushki goreli glaza, chtoby ona ukrashala Vashu zhizn' iarkimi kraskami, nado ee liubit', kruzhit', zashchishchat', balovat' i tselovat', a eshche pokupat' shariki i vatu, budto Vam 16.  Ona ne rebionok, no vysshee schast'e, kogda ona chuvstvuet sebia Diuimovochkoi na vashikh sil'nykh rukakh, obnimaia liubimye plechi, kotorye dariat ei spokoistvie, stabil'nost' i uverennost'. Ia vizhu tol'ko takoe budushee. Inache zachem eto vse? S plokhim muzhchinoi zhenshchina slabee, chem bez nego. S khoroshim ne znaet granits, no chuvstvuet garmoniiu i pokoriaet mir.

Kazhdogo iz nas obshchestvo assotsiiruet s kakimi-to obrazami i patternami. Ia schitaiu, chto zadacha liuboi tvorcheskoi lichnosti sniat' vse okovy, predubezhdeniia, chto ty ne ponravish'sia, tebia ne poimut i osudiat.  V tvorchestve ne dolzhno byt' granits, a dlia etogo nado vsem izbavliat'sia ot raznogo roda strakhov. Tvorcheskii chelovek dolzhen byt' svobodnym vnutri, slovno rebionok, kotoryi fantaziruet i ne znaet slova <<nevozmozhno>>. Mne kazhetsia, eta svoboda razvivaet kharizmu i pritiagivaet so vremenem vnimanie obshchestva. Aktior - eto ne korochka universiteta i zvanie imenitogo mastera. Aktior - eto chelovek, kotoryi znaet, chego khochet, kotoryi liubit zhizn' i kazhdyi den' ee otkryvaet s goriashchimi glazami. Mne kazhetsia, schast'e tvorcheskoi dushi - eto ponimat' i otkryto zaiavliat' - kto ty, k chemu chuvstvuesh' pritiazhenie i v chem oshchushchaesh' svoi potentsial. Glavnoe - ne boiat'sia priznat'sia v etom miru. Puskai tebe 60, ty rabotaesh' santekhnikom, a khochesh' byt' stendaperom i ne remontirovat', a shutit' pro unitazy. Delai eto) Vozmozhno, ty edinstvennyi v mire mozhesh' tak smeshno i tonko poshutit' pro rakoviny. Vot predstav'te, chelovek vsiu zhizn' vozilsia s boltami, a potom prosnulsia i ponial, chto teper' <<bolty>> v ego zhizni budut tol'ko v iumore. Pochemu net? Ia za liubye tvorcheskie eksperimenty i nachinaniia. Glavnoe probovat' i pozakryvat' vse geshtal'ty, poka eto slovosochetanie eshchio v trendakh

Quando o corpo adoece ou tem mais tendencia a adoecer dizemos que ha uma deficiencia de Wei Qi. Esta e a energia defensiva do nosso corpo que impede ou dificulta a instalacao de doencas. Em periodos de alta incidencia de infeccoes por agentes patologicos ou por modificacoes bruscas de temperatura faz-se  necessario buscar formas de prevencao fortalecendo esse nosso campo energetico, especialmente atraves da alimentacao saudavel e evitando situacoes estressantes ou de risco. A acupuntura e a auriculoterapia sao de extrema valia especialmente na PREVENCAO dessas ocorrencias pois atuam diretamente sobre os campos energeticos do corpo e estimulam a liberacao de substancias protetoras pelos orgaos internos, harmonizando assim todo sistema de defesa. Lembrando que estes tratamentos, a depender do agente, podem nao evitar totalmente a contaminacao, especialmente quando sao agentes fisicos, porem reduzem bastante os sintomas e ajudam na recuperacao. Um corpo preparado possui menor probabilidade de sofrer alteracoes estruturais pelas doencas sazonais e pandemias! Prevenir e sempre o melhor remedio. Obs: lave as maos com frequencia! Sentindo-se doente procure uma unidade de saude e evite aglomeracoes de pessoas em respeito ao proximo.
